INSERT INTO `servers_details` VALUES ('0', 'Joao Pessoa', 'Brazil', 'We\'re pretty sure this server is in Rio, it\'s surprisingly difficult to sign up for a server in a different country, in a language you don\'t speak.<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;q=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;sll=52.258071,4.828491&amp;sspn=1.819108,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;cd=1&amp;geocode=FQ2Fov4djaxs_Q&amp;split=0&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;ll=-14.51978,-44.296875&amp;spn=29.470766,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;q=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;sll=52.258071,4.828491&amp;sspn=1.819108,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;cd=1&amp;geocode=FQ2Fov4djaxs_Q&amp;split=0&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;ll=-14.51978,-44.296875&amp;spn=29.470766,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys surfing, lazy afternoons on the beach, and enjoying the local produce.  It\'s ideal for testing your GeoIP applications throughout South America.\r\n', 'Nous sommes pas mal sûr que ce serveur est à Rio de Janeiro, au Brésil, mais il est étonnant à quel point c’est difficile d’acheter un serveur dans une langue étranger.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;q=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;sll=52.258071,4.828491&amp;sspn=1.819108,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;cd=1&amp;geocode=FQ2Fov4djaxs_Q&amp;split=0&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;ll=-14.51978,-44.296875&amp;spn=29.470766,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;q=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;sll=52.258071,4.828491&amp;sspn=1.819108,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;cd=1&amp;geocode=FQ2Fov4djaxs_Q&amp;split=0&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rio+de+Janeiro+-+RJ,+Brazil&amp;ll=-14.51978,-44.296875&amp;spn=29.470766,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur aime faire du surf, flâner sur la plage, et manger les fruits locaux.  Il est idéal pour tester vos applications GeoIP à travers l’Amérique du Sud.'), ('1', 'Melbourne', 'Australia', 'This server is located in or about Sydney Australia. <br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Sydney,+Australia&amp;sll=35.924645,137.878418&amp;sspn=19.20872,24.367676&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Sydney+NSW,+Australia&amp;ll=-31.090574,151.391602&amp;spn=13.152947,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Sydney,+Australia&amp;sll=35.924645,137.878418&amp;sspn=19.20872,24.367676&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Sydney+NSW,+Australia&amp;ll=-31.090574,151.391602&amp;spn=13.152947,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nIts hobbies include enjoying music at the nearby Opera house, as well as photography in the outback.  It provides excellent coverage for GeoIP testing in Australia, along with our Brisbane server.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Sydney, en Australie.\n\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Sydney,+Australia&amp;sll=35.924645,137.878418&amp;sspn=19.20872,24.367676&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Sydney+NSW,+Australia&amp;ll=-31.090574,151.391602&amp;spn=13.152947,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Sydney,+Australia&amp;sll=35.924645,137.878418&amp;sspn=19.20872,24.367676&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Sydney+NSW,+Australia&amp;ll=-31.090574,151.391602&amp;spn=13.152947,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nComme passe-temps, ce serveur aime écouter la musique au Sydney Opera House, la photographie dans le outback australien.  Il est une excellente option pour tester les applications GeoIP en Australie, tout comme notre serveur à Brisbane.\n'), ('2', 'Toronto', 'Canada', 'This proxy server is located in the popular Front Street data center in downtown Toronto, Canada, the capital of the province of Ontario. It provdes the perfect point for testing GeoIP application performance from within Canada, as well as more granular data from within Toronto. Some GeoIP providers may falsely report that this server is in Ottawa, don\'t be alarmed. <br><br>\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"650\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;sll=43.64501,-79.383798&amp;sspn=0.006817,0.014806&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;ll=43.698658,-79.394073&amp;spn=0.173752,0.44632&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;sll=43.64501,-79.383798&amp;sspn=0.006817,0.014806&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;ll=43.698658,-79.394073&amp;spn=0.173752,0.44632&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nThis server\'s hobbies include calculating random digits of pi, then using that information to design cross stitch patterns. There\'s a rather cute coaster the server is quite proud of sitting nearby for late night coding sessions. ', 'Ce serveur se situe dans la centre de données prestigieuse sur la rue Front, à Toronto, la ville capitale de l’Ontario, et la plus grande ville du Canada.  Il est une excellent option pour tester les applications GeoIP au Canada en général, et plus précissément au Toronto.  Certaines compagnies d’identifiation vont vous dire que le serveur est à Ottawa, mais n’inquietez-vous pas, il est bel et bien à Toronto.\n\n<iframe width=\"650\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;sll=43.64501,-79.383798&amp;sspn=0.006817,0.014806&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;ll=43.698658,-79.394073&amp;spn=0.173752,0.44632&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;sll=43.64501,-79.383798&amp;sspn=0.006817,0.014806&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=151+Front+St+W,+Toronto,+Toronto+Division,+Ontario,+Canada&amp;ll=43.698658,-79.394073&amp;spn=0.173752,0.44632&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime créer des motifs de broderie basées sur des chiffres de pi choisi au hasard.  Il est très fier d’une soucoupe sur une table à proximité qui attend des nuits blanches de codage.\n'), ('3', 'Prague', 'Czech Republic', 'This server is located in Prague within the Czech Republic. The native name for the city is Praha. Many billing agents regard the Czech Republic as a high risk country for credit card transactions, so it provides an excellent location to test those aspects of your GeoIP-aware application.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,Praha+3+&amp;sll=50.068516,14.440446&amp;sspn=0.05961,0.095186&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,+130+00+Prague+3,+Czech+Republic&amp;ll=50.666872,14.205322&amp;spn=2.437295,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,Praha+3+&amp;sll=50.068516,14.440446&amp;sspn=0.05961,0.095186&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,+130+00+Prague+3,+Czech+Republic&amp;ll=50.666872,14.205322&amp;spn=2.437295,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server loves exploring the National Muzem that\'s just around the corner, and stopping in for a quick bite of Veprove Knedliky after a hard day of proxying traffic. ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Prague, dans la République Czech. 	Son nom Czech est Praha.  La République Czech est considéré par beaucoup de compagnies de traitement de carte de crédit d’être une région avec risque de fraude élevée; ce serveur vous offre une bonne opportunité de tester cette partie de votre application GeoIP.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,Praha+3+&amp;sll=50.068516,14.440446&amp;sspn=0.05961,0.095186&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,+130+00+Prague+3,+Czech+Republic&amp;ll=50.666872,14.205322&amp;spn=2.437295,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,Praha+3+&amp;sll=50.068516,14.440446&amp;sspn=0.05961,0.095186&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vinohradsk%C3%A1+190,+130+00+Prague+3,+Czech+Republic&amp;ll=50.666872,14.205322&amp;spn=2.437295,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur aime explorer le musée nationale qui est à deux pas de son centre de données, et manger le Veprove Knedliky après les longues journées dirigeant les données.'), ('4', 'Paris', 'France', 'This server located in or about Paris provides our presence in France. Does your GeoIP application detect French customers and provide the correct pricing and language options? WonderProxy can help make sure!<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=paris+france&amp;sll=-13.581921,-59.326172&amp;sspn=84.133211,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Paris,+%C3%8Ele-de-France,+France&amp;ll=50.233152,1.757813&amp;spn=4.919967,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=paris+france&amp;sll=-13.581921,-59.326172&amp;sspn=84.133211,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Paris,+%C3%8Ele-de-France,+France&amp;ll=50.233152,1.757813&amp;spn=4.919967,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys relaxing afternoons at the cafe and exploring portions of the Louvre off the beaten track. ', 'Ce serveur situé à (ou près de) Paris offre une partie de notre présence Française, avec Roubaix. Est-ce que votre applications offre les options linguistiques appropriés pour ce pays?  WonderProxy peut vous aider à vous assurer.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=paris+france&amp;sll=-13.581921,-59.326172&amp;sspn=84.133211,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Paris,+%C3%8Ele-de-France,+France&amp;ll=50.233152,1.757813&amp;spn=4.919967,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=paris+france&amp;sll=-13.581921,-59.326172&amp;sspn=84.133211,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Paris,+%C3%8Ele-de-France,+France&amp;ll=50.233152,1.757813&amp;spn=4.919967,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur aime passer l’après-midi au café, et explorer les parties moins-connus du Louvre.'), ('5', 'Berlin', 'Germany', 'Our server located in Hanover, Germany provides part of our presence within that country, alongside our Frankfurt server. The hostname was chosen for the larger and more recongnizable city nearby.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Am+Mittelfelde+29,++30519+Hannover&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Am+Mittelfelde,+30519+Hanover,+Lower+Saxony,+Germany&amp;ll=53.034607,9.052734&amp;spn=2.312373,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Am+Mittelfelde+29,++30519+Hannover&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Am+Mittelfelde,+30519+Hanover,+Lower+Saxony,+Germany&amp;ll=53.034607,9.052734&amp;spn=2.312373,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server\'s hobbies include photography, and taking trips to explore the black forest.  It is an excellent option for testing applications that use GeoIP targeted at Germany.', 'Notre serveur à Hanovre en Allemagne n’est qu’une moitié de notre réseau allemand, avec l’autre moitié à Frankfurt.  Le nom était choisi pour la ville mieux-connue à proximité (soit Berlin).<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Am+Mittelfelde+29,++30519+Hannover&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Am+Mittelfelde,+30519+Hanover,+Lower+Saxony,+Germany&amp;ll=53.034607,9.052734&amp;spn=2.312373,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Am+Mittelfelde+29,++30519+Hannover&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Am+Mittelfelde,+30519+Hanover,+Lower+Saxony,+Germany&amp;ll=53.034607,9.052734&amp;spn=2.312373,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nLes passes-temps de ce serveur incluent la photographie, et la randonnée dans la Forêt Noir.  Il est une excellente option pour tester des applications GeoIP ciblé pour l’Allemagne.'), ('6', 'Tokyo', 'Japan', 'This server located in Tokyo provides WonderProxy\'s presence in Japan, as well as a great access point for those accessing the Pacific rim and wanting to test their applicaton\'s GeoIP capabilities in that region. Automatic handling of multi-byte character sets (which are the norm for Logogram-based written languages) provide a challange for many developers. Test your application\'s handling of those sets through an appropriate proxy.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tokyo,+Japan&amp;sll=48.856667,2.350987&amp;sspn=0.244411,0.380745&amp;g=paris+france&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=T%C5%8Dky%C5%8D+Metropolis,+Japan&amp;ll=38.030786,139.460449&amp;spn=6.056499,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tokyo,+Japan&amp;sll=48.856667,2.350987&amp;sspn=0.244411,0.380745&amp;g=paris+france&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=T%C5%8Dky%C5%8D+Metropolis,+Japan&amp;ll=38.030786,139.460449&amp;spn=6.056499,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys cute meals from bento boxes, as well as an unhealthy obsession with American comic books.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Tokyo, notre serveur en Japon, et est une excellente option pour ceux qui ont des applications GeoIP ciblées à la région du Pacifique.  Il est souvent difficile à faire fonctionner les applications existantes dans un environnement multi-octets (tel les langues avec écriture logographique)—vous pouvez vérifier votre application en vous servant d’une proxie comme celui-ci.\n\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tokyo,+Japan&amp;sll=48.856667,2.350987&amp;sspn=0.244411,0.380745&amp;g=paris+france&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=T%C5%8Dky%C5%8D+Metropolis,+Japan&amp;ll=38.030786,139.460449&amp;spn=6.056499,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tokyo,+Japan&amp;sll=48.856667,2.350987&amp;sspn=0.244411,0.380745&amp;g=paris+france&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=T%C5%8Dky%C5%8D+Metropolis,+Japan&amp;ll=38.030786,139.460449&amp;spn=6.056499,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime manger des repas adorables en boîte bento et a une obsession pour les bandes dessinées Américaines.\n'), ('7', 'Amsterdam', 'Netherlands', 'This server is located in Haarlemmermeer, Netherlands which is basically a suburb of Amsterdam. It\'s located surprisingly close to the Schipol airport, providing the WonderProxy presence within the Netherlands.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Haarlemmermeer,+Netherlands&amp;sll=-43.2932,174.506836&amp;sspn=34.526178,48.735352&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Haarlemmermeer,+North+Holland,+The+Netherlands&amp;ll=52.419173,4.515381&amp;spn=0.586282,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Haarlemmermeer,+Netherlands&amp;sll=-43.2932,174.506836&amp;sspn=34.526178,48.735352&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Haarlemmermeer,+North+Holland,+The+Netherlands&amp;ll=52.419173,4.515381&amp;spn=0.586282,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys handing out bad directions to the red light district to anyone who refers to the country as \"Holland\", which is actually just a province of the Netherlands.  It\'s an excellent server for testing out applicatons\' GeoIP capabilities within the Netherlands, and indeed within Holland more specifically.  ', 'Ce serveur est situé à Haarlemmermeer, aux Pays-Bas, une banlieue d’Amsterdam.  En fait, il est à deux pas de l’aéroport Schipol, et il fournit la présence WodnerProxy aux Pays-Bas.\r<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Haarlemmermeer,+Pays-Bas&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=52.370216,4.895168&amp;sspn=0.113823,0.308647&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;g=amsterdam&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Haarlemmermeer,+Hollande-Septentrionale,+Pays-Bas&amp;t=m&amp;ll=54.597528,4.086914&amp;spn=8.919107,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Haarlemmermeer,+Pays-Bas&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=52.370216,4.895168&amp;sspn=0.113823,0.308647&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;g=amsterdam&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Haarlemmermeer,+Hollande-Septentrionale,+Pays-Bas&amp;t=m&amp;ll=54.597528,4.086914&amp;spn=8.919107,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\rPour passer le temps, ce serveur s’amuse à mal-diriger toutes les personnes qui réfèrent à l’Hollande (qui n’est qu’une province) au lieu des Pays-Bas quand elles cherchent le quartier rouge.\r'), ('8', 'Wellington', 'New Zealand', 'This server is located in Albany, a smaller town just north of Auckland.  It\'s an excellent option for testing out GeoIP-aware applications targeted at New Zealand.  It\'s named after some great people who have been instrumental to the success of WonderProxy who hail from Wellington.<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Albany,+New+Zealand&amp;sll=-36.727033,174.698032&amp;sspn=0.074434,0.095186&amp;g=Albany,+New+Zealand&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Albany,+New+Zealand&amp;ll=-31.728167,166.376953&amp;spn=26.023071,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Albany,+New+Zealand&amp;sll=-36.727033,174.698032&amp;sspn=0.074434,0.095186&amp;g=Albany,+New+Zealand&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Albany,+New+Zealand&amp;ll=-31.728167,166.376953&amp;spn=26.023071,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys picturesque walks through the hills while telling tourists fictional stories about the filming of Lord of the Rings. It may insist that it was in the Weta encoding farm, this is false.  ', null), ('9', 'Moscow', 'Russian Federation', 'This server is located in or about Moscow. Russia is considered to be a high risk country for fraud by many credit card processing agencies, as such this proxy provides an excellent place to test that element of your code base, as well as elements utilizing GeoIP. \r\n\r\nThis server owns a rather nice <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ushanka\">Ushanka</a> and loathes \"In Soviet Russia ____ you!\" jokes. ', 'Ce serveur se situe à (ou en proximité de) Moscou.  La Russie est considéré par beaucoup de compagnies de traitement de carte de crédit d’être un région d’haute risque de fraude; ce serveur vous offre une bonne opportunité de tester ce partie de votre code, et les applications GeoIP.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Moscow,+Russia&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Russian+Federation,+Moscow&amp;ll=55.756486,37.617188&amp;spn=0.540939,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Moscow,+Russia&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Russian+Federation,+Moscow&amp;ll=55.756486,37.617188&amp;spn=0.540939,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur se vante d’être propriétaire d’une magnifique Ushanka, et déteste les blagues « In soviet russie —— you ».\n'), ('10', 'Stockholm', 'Sweden', 'This server is located in Hammarby Sjöstad, Sweden. A great area just south of Stockholm. This server provides WonderProxy\'s Scandanavian presence, and opportunity for testing GeoIP applications\' performance in Scandanavia.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Sweden&amp;sll=48.078079,-123.370972&amp;sspn=3.971214,6.091919&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Stockholm,+Sweden&amp;ll=59.453452,17.984619&amp;spn=0.488574,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Sweden&amp;sll=48.078079,-123.370972&amp;sspn=3.971214,6.091919&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Stockholm,+Sweden&amp;ll=59.453452,17.984619&amp;spn=0.488574,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server\'s principal hobby is taking long walks in the mountains, always on the lookout for Hjortron (cloudberry) which it puts into its award winning jams and baked goods. It dislikes the \"Swedish Meatballs\" served by Ikea. \r\n', 'Ce serveur se situe à Hammarby Sjöstad, au Suède, une belle région au Sud du Stockholm. Ce serveur offre une partie de notre réseau scandinave, avec nos serveurs à Helsinki, et Copenhague., une autre bonne option pour tester les applications GeoIP en Scandivanie.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Sweden&amp;sll=48.078079,-123.370972&amp;sspn=3.971214,6.091919&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Stockholm,+Sweden&amp;ll=59.453452,17.984619&amp;spn=0.488574,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Sweden&amp;sll=48.078079,-123.370972&amp;sspn=3.971214,6.091919&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Hammarby+Sj%C3%B6stad,+Stockholm,+Sweden&amp;ll=59.453452,17.984619&amp;spn=0.488574,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur aime faire du randonné dans les montagnes, toujours à la recherche du Hjortron (« chicouté / faux mûrier »), qu’il utilise dans ses confitures et gâteaux gagnantes.  Il déteste les « boulettes suèdoises » d’Ikea.'), ('11', 'London', 'United Kingdom', 'This server resides in the Telehouse North datacenter in the London Docklands area. Does your application properly display prices in Pounds Sterling?  Do your geo-referent applications use GeoIP correctly? Only with this server can you tell for sure!\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=London,+UK&amp;sll=51.560851,0.047379&amp;sspn=0.361991,0.679092&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Westminster,+London,+United+Kingdom&amp;ll=51.520707,-0.148315&amp;spn=0.074769,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=London,+UK&amp;sll=51.560851,0.047379&amp;sspn=0.361991,0.679092&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Westminster,+London,+United+Kingdom&amp;ll=51.520707,-0.148315&amp;spn=0.074769,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server occupies its days drinking loose leaf earl grey tea, while making scones on the CPU heat sink. These scones are then served to hungry technicians to ensure the highest quality of service. \r\n', 'Ce serveur se situe dans la centre de données Telehouse North dans la région des Docklands de Londres.  Est-ce que votre application note les prix en £?  Est-ce que vos applications avec ciblage géographique se servent du GeoIP correctement?  Avec ce serveur vous pouvez vous assurer de ces réponses.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=London,+UK&amp;sll=51.560851,0.047379&amp;sspn=0.361991,0.679092&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Westminster,+London,+United+Kingdom&amp;ll=51.520707,-0.148315&amp;spn=0.074769,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=London,+UK&amp;sll=51.560851,0.047379&amp;sspn=0.361991,0.679092&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Westminster,+London,+United+Kingdom&amp;ll=51.520707,-0.148315&amp;spn=0.074769,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur passe sa journée en buvant du thé Earl Grey en attendant que ses scones cuisent sur le dissipateur.  Les scones sont donnés aux techniciens pour assurer d’un niveau de service technique élevé.\n'), ('12', 'Dallas', 'United States', 'This server is located in Dallas, Texas. We could tell you more than that, but then we\'d have to tickle that information right back out of you.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Dallas,+Texas&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Dallas,+Texas&amp;ll=33.385586,-97.536621&amp;spn=3.210464,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Dallas,+Texas&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Dallas,+Texas&amp;ll=33.385586,-97.536621&amp;spn=3.210464,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server occupies its time perfecting pulled pork recepies it finds on the internet, and trying to sneak out a signal to tell you exactly where it lives.  It\'s an excellent choice for testing GeoIP-using applications targeted at the US south or south-west.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Dallas, au Texas.  Nous pourrions élaborer, mais dans ce cas, nous serions obligés de vous chatouiller jusqu’au moment que vous oubliez.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Dallas,+Texas&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Dallas,+Texas&amp;ll=33.385586,-97.536621&amp;spn=3.210464,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Dallas,+Texas&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Dallas,+Texas&amp;ll=33.385586,-97.536621&amp;spn=3.210464,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nCe serveur passe son temps à perfectionner les recettes qu’il retrouve sur l’Internet pour le porc tiré, et avec les attentas d’envoyer un signal pour vous dire où exactement il vie.  C’est une excellente option pour vérifier les applications GeoIP ciblées au Sud/Sud-Ouest des États-Unis.'), ('13', 'New York', 'United States', 'This server is located in Manhatten, New York. This is the most populated city in the United States. The server itself rests in a data center in the financial district. <br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=75+Broad+Street+New+York,+New+York,+10004,+US+&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=75+Broad+St,+New+York,+10004&amp;ll=40.730869,-73.998413&amp;spn=0.091057,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=75+Broad+Street+New+York,+New+York,+10004,+US+&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=75+Broad+St,+New+York,+10004&amp;ll=40.730869,-73.998413&amp;spn=0.091057,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis servers hobbies include exploring central park, seeing off broadway shows, and riding the subway.  If you\'re writing applications targeted at New York, this is a great server for testing their use of GeoIP.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Manhattan, à New York (à New York, aux Etats-Unis).  C’est la plus grande ville des Etats-Unis.  Il vit dans une centre de données dans le quartier financier.\n\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=75+Broad+Street+New+York,+New+York,+10004,+US+&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=75+Broad+St,+New+York,+10004&amp;ll=40.730869,-73.998413&amp;spn=0.091057,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=75+Broad+Street+New+York,+New+York,+10004,+US+&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=75+Broad+St,+New+York,+10004&amp;ll=40.730869,-73.998413&amp;spn=0.091057,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime explorer Central Park, voir des comédies musicales sur Broadway, et prendre le subway.  Si vous écrivez des applications ciblées à New York, c’est une excellente serveur pour tester le GeoIP.'), ('14', 'Boston', 'United States', '', ''), ('15', 'Miami', 'United States', 'A great server located in Miami Florida. It was originally mour second East Coast location, after Washington, and is a good choice for testing applications using GeoIP in Florida.<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Miami,+Florida&amp;sll=55.755786,37.617633&amp;sspn=1.672335,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Miami,+Miami-Dade,+Florida&amp;ll=27.527758,-79.980469&amp;spn=6.816841,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Miami,+Florida&amp;sll=55.755786,37.617633&amp;sspn=1.672335,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Miami,+Miami-Dade,+Florida&amp;ll=27.527758,-79.980469&amp;spn=6.816841,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys cool, air-conditioned server rooms, and high speed data connections. It rests happy :).', 'Ce serveur se situe à Miami, en Floride.  Il était notre deuxième option sur le côte Est Américaine, après Washington, et est une bonne option pour tester les applications en Floride.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Miami,+Florida&amp;sll=55.755786,37.617633&amp;sspn=1.672335,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Miami,+Miami-Dade,+Florida&amp;ll=27.527758,-79.980469&amp;spn=6.816841,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Miami,+Florida&amp;sll=55.755786,37.617633&amp;sspn=1.672335,3.045959&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Miami,+Miami-Dade,+Florida&amp;ll=27.527758,-79.980469&amp;spn=6.816841,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime les locaux de serveurs bien-climatisés, et les connections rapides. \n\n'), ('16', 'Washington', 'United States', 'This server is located between Dulles airport and Washington, DC itself, hence the name. Well, that, and not too many people have heard of Herndon, though it\'s quite nice. This is a great server on the East coast, near several major metropoliton areas and an ideal option for testing applications\' use of GeoIP on the east coast.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=+2350+Corporate+Park+Drive+Herndon+VA&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=2350+Corporate+Park+Dr,+Herndon,+Fairfax,+Virginia+20171&amp;ll=39.022384,-77.294312&amp;spn=0.373418,0.858307&amp;z=10&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=+2350+Corporate+Park+Drive+Herndon+VA&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=2350+Corporate+Park+Dr,+Herndon,+Fairfax,+Virginia+20171&amp;ll=39.022384,-77.294312&amp;spn=0.373418,0.858307&amp;z=10&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys attempting to use a paper clip to attach computer rights amendments to various bills in congress (if only it had legs, this would be much easier).', 'Ce serveur se situe entre l’aéroport Dulles, et Washington D.C. elle-même (d’où son nom)—le fait que peu de personnes connait Herndon (on me dit que c’est une belle ville, par exemple) s’implique aussi.  Il est un excellent serveur dans l’Est Américaine, près de plusieurs métropoles et une option idéale pour tester les applications GeoIP.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=+2350+Corporate+Park+Drive+Herndon+VA&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=2350+Corporate+Park+Dr,+Herndon,+Fairfax,+Virginia+20171&amp;ll=39.022384,-77.294312&amp;spn=0.373418,0.858307&amp;z=10&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=+2350+Corporate+Park+Drive+Herndon+VA&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=73.049727,97.470703&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=2350+Corporate+Park+Dr,+Herndon,+Fairfax,+Virginia+20171&amp;ll=39.022384,-77.294312&amp;spn=0.373418,0.858307&amp;z=10&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur aime essayer d’utiliser des trombones pour attacher des amendements promouvant les droits d’ordinateurs aux projets de lois du Congrès Américaine (s’il avait des jambes, ça serait beaucoup plus facile).\n'), ('17', 'Barcelona', 'Spain', 'This server, located in beautiful Barcelona, Spain provides our Spanish access point, as well as another element of our European presence.  If you\'ve been wondering if your GeoIP-aware applications are correctly identifying Spanish users, this is the server for you!<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?client=opera&amp;q=barcelona,+spain&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Barcelona,+Catalonia,+Spain&amp;gl=ca&amp;ei=b4MyS8jMJo_clAeikemnBw&amp;ved=0CA0Q8gEwAA&amp;ll=41.603121,2.092896&amp;spn=1.437645,3.433228&amp;z=8&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?client=opera&amp;q=barcelona,+spain&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Barcelona,+Catalonia,+Spain&amp;gl=ca&amp;ei=b4MyS8jMJo_clAeikemnBw&amp;ved=0CA0Q8gEwAA&amp;ll=41.603121,2.092896&amp;spn=1.437645,3.433228&amp;z=8&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys surfing, long walks on the beach, but abhors the rain. ', 'Ce serveur, situé dans la belle ville de Barcelone, en Espagne, représente un point d’accès espagnol, et une partie de notre réseau européen.  Si vous voulez vérifier si vos applications GeoIP identifient les visiteurs espagnols correctement, cet serveur est parfait pour vous.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?client=opera&amp;q=barcelona,+spain&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Barcelona,+Catalonia,+Spain&amp;gl=ca&amp;ei=b4MyS8jMJo_clAeikemnBw&amp;ved=0CA0Q8gEwAA&amp;ll=41.603121,2.092896&amp;spn=1.437645,3.433228&amp;z=8&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?client=opera&amp;q=barcelona,+spain&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Barcelona,+Catalonia,+Spain&amp;gl=ca&amp;ei=b4MyS8jMJo_clAeikemnBw&amp;ved=0CA0Q8gEwAA&amp;ll=41.603121,2.092896&amp;spn=1.437645,3.433228&amp;z=8&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur aime faire du surf, et prendre des longues marches sur la plage; mais il déteste la pluie.'), ('18', 'Atlanta', 'United States', 'This server is located in Atlanta, Georgia in the United States. It provides great granular geoip testing to users looking for very specific targeting in the U.S.A.\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?client=opera&amp;q=atlanta,+georgia&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Atlanta,+Fulton,+Georgia,+United+States&amp;gl=ca&amp;ei=DPhgS5rwHM_slAe4_PjmCw&amp;ved=0CAsQ8gEwAA&amp;ll=33.80825,-84.437485&amp;spn=0.199688,0.429153&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?client=opera&amp;q=atlanta,+georgia&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Atlanta,+Fulton,+Georgia,+United+States&amp;gl=ca&amp;ei=DPhgS5rwHM_slAe4_PjmCw&amp;ved=0CAsQ8gEwAA&amp;ll=33.80825,-84.437485&amp;spn=0.199688,0.429153&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>This server\'s hobbies include riding the mechanical bull at the local watering hole, and eating cotton candy at the county fair. ', 'Ce serveur est situé à Atlanta, Géorgie, aux Etats-Unis.  Il est idéal pour ceux qui veulent tester les applications géoIP avec un ciblage très précis dans les États-Unis.\r<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Atlanta,+G%C3%A9orgie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=52.882391,5.471191&amp;sspn=7.202305,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Atlanta,+Comt%C3%A9+de+Fulton,+G%C3%A9orgie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.371135,-84.396973&amp;spn=6.269372,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Atlanta,+G%C3%A9orgie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=52.882391,5.471191&amp;sspn=7.202305,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Atlanta,+Comt%C3%A9+de+Fulton,+G%C3%A9orgie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.371135,-84.396973&amp;spn=6.269372,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\rComme passes-temps, ce serveur aime monter le taureau rodéos mécanique du bar près de chez-lui, et manger du barbe à papa aux foires.\r'), ('19', 'Newmarket', 'Ireland', 'This server is located in Newmarket, Ireland and is a perfect server for specific GeoIP testing within Ireland.<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=newmarket,+ireland&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=81.878541,86.132812&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Newmarket,+County+Cork,+Ireland&amp;ll=52.213234,-9.001035&amp;spn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;z=14&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=newmarket,+ireland&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=81.878541,86.132812&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Newmarket,+County+Cork,+Ireland&amp;ll=52.213234,-9.001035&amp;spn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;z=14\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server enjoys lazy afternoons, drinking Kilkenny beer and reading historical fiction. ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Newmarket, en Irelande, et est une excellente option pour tester les applications en Irelande.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=newmarket,+ireland&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=81.878541,86.132812&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Newmarket,+County+Cork,+Ireland&amp;ll=52.213234,-9.001035&amp;spn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;z=14&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=newmarket,+ireland&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=81.878541,86.132812&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Newmarket,+County+Cork,+Ireland&amp;ll=52.213234,-9.001035&amp;spn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;z=14\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\nCe serveur aime les après-midis calmes, boire du Kilkenny et lire le romans historiques.\n'), ('20', 'Vienna', 'Austria', 'This server is located in Vienna, Austria.<br><br>\r\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=vienna,+austria&amp;sll=52.213234,-9.001064&amp;sspn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vienna,+Austria&amp;ll=48.226502,16.375809&amp;spn=0.080051,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=vienna,+austria&amp;sll=52.213234,-9.001064&amp;sspn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vienna,+Austria&amp;ll=48.226502,16.375809&amp;spn=0.080051,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThis server\'s hobbies include hiking in the mountains, dominos, and a strange facination with pop tarts.  It dreams of one day attending the Vienna Opera Ball.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Vienne, en Autriche.\n\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=vienna,+austria&amp;sll=52.213234,-9.001064&amp;sspn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vienna,+Austria&amp;ll=48.226502,16.375809&amp;spn=0.080051,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=vienna,+austria&amp;sll=52.213234,-9.001064&amp;sspn=0.064581,0.084114&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Vienna,+Austria&amp;ll=48.226502,16.375809&amp;spn=0.080051,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nSes passe-temps préférés incluent le randonné à pieds, jouer aux dominos, et manger des pop-tarts.  Il rêve d’aller au Bal de l’Opéra de Vienne.\n'), ('21', 'Brisbane', 'Australia', 'This server is located in sunny Brisbane, Australia, and provides a second Aussie server option alongside Sydney.  <br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brisbane+QLD,+Australia&amp;sll=42.309308,-88.498993&amp;sspn=0.328538,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Brisbane+Queensland,+Australia&amp;ll=-27.279043,153.020325&amp;spn=0.847073,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brisbane+QLD,+Australia&amp;sll=42.309308,-88.498993&amp;sspn=0.328538,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Brisbane+Queensland,+Australia&amp;ll=-27.279043,153.020325&amp;spn=0.847073,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\n<br><br>\nThis server\'s hobbies include watching Australian rules football, surfing, and having barbecues on the beach - all effective solutions to the impressive temperatures it experiences in the summer.  Thank goodness it has air conditioning.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Brisbane, en Australie, et est une moitié de notre réseau australien, avec Sydney.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brisbane+QLD,+Australia&amp;sll=42.309308,-88.498993&amp;sspn=0.328538,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Brisbane+Queensland,+Australia&amp;ll=-27.279043,153.020325&amp;spn=0.847073,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brisbane+QLD,+Australia&amp;sll=42.309308,-88.498993&amp;sspn=0.328538,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Brisbane+Queensland,+Australia&amp;ll=-27.279043,153.020325&amp;spn=0.847073,1.716614&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nComme passe-temps, ce serveur aime écouter le football Australian, faire du surf, et piqueniquer sur la plage – des bonnes solutions à la chaleur intense d’un été australien.  Il est très heureux d’avoir l’air climatisé.\n'), ('22', 'Chicago', 'United States', 'This server is located in the Chicago Board of Trade Building in downton Chicago, Illinois.  <br><br>\n<img src=\"https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=41.877708,-87.632275&zoom=13&size=625x350&markers=color:blue|label:W|141+W+Jackson+Blvd,+Chicago,+Cook,+Illinois+60604&sensor=false\"><br /><small><a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=141+West+Jackson+Boulevard,+Chicago,+IL+60604,+United+States&amp;sll=41.877708,-87.632275&amp;sspn=0.041348,0.066175&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=141+W+Jackson+Blvd,+Chicago,+Cook,+Illinois+60604&amp;ll=41.886816,-87.638798&amp;spn=0.044345,0.107288&amp;z=13&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\n<br><br>\nThis server enjoys competeing with Wellington for the title of \'Server in the Windiest City.\'  When not measuring windspeeds, it enjoys watching Oprah in hopes of seeing itself - so far it has been left disappointed.', 'Ce serveur se situe dans l’édifice Chicago Board of Trade dans le centre-ville de Chicago, en Illinois.<br><br>\n<img src=\"https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=41.877708,-87.632275&zoom=13&size=625x350&markers=color:blue|label:W|141+W+Jackson+Blvd,+Chicago,+Cook,+Illinois+60604&sensor=false\"><br /><small><a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=141+West+Jackson+Boulevard,+Chicago,+IL+60604,+United+States&amp;sll=41.877708,-87.632275&amp;sspn=0.041348,0.066175&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=141+W+Jackson+Blvd,+Chicago,+Cook,+Illinois+60604&amp;ll=41.886816,-87.638798&amp;spn=0.044345,0.107288&amp;z=13&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime faire des compétitions avec Wellington pour le titre de « Serveur avec la ville le plus venteuse ». Lorsqu’il ne mesure pas ses vitesses de rafales, il aime écouter Oprah en espérant se voir – jusqu’à maintenant il reste déçu.\n'), ('23', 'San Jose', 'United States', 'This server is located in Santa Clara California, near the Norman Y Mineta San Jose International Airport.  <br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=santa+clara&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santa+Clara,+California&amp;ll=37.367702,-121.938629&amp;spn=0.094682,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=santa+clara&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santa+Clara,+California&amp;ll=37.367702,-121.938629&amp;spn=0.094682,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis sever enjoys the smug satisfaction of knowing that unlike the other WonderProxy servers, it alone is nestled in Silicon Valley.  It also likes walking in the many parks outside of San Jose and smelling the sea breezes coming off the Pacific. ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Santa Clara en California, à proximité de l’Aéroport Internationale Norman Y Mineta San Jose.  <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=santa+clara&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santa+Clara,+California&amp;ll=37.367702,-121.938629&amp;spn=0.094682,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=santa+clara&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santa+Clara,+California&amp;ll=37.367702,-121.938629&amp;spn=0.094682,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur se vante d’être le seul serveur de WonderProxy à Silicon Valley.  Il aime se promener dans les parcs près de San Jose et sentir les vents océaniques du Pacifique.'), ('24', 'Seattle', 'United States', 'This server is located in Seattle, Washington and offers great connectivity to the west coast of the USA and Asia Pacific.  <br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=seattle&amp;sll=37.351601,-121.924896&amp;sspn=0.176577,0.264702&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ll=47.620975,-122.34478&amp;spn=0.080299,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=seattle&amp;sll=37.351601,-121.924896&amp;sspn=0.176577,0.264702&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ll=47.620975,-122.34478&amp;spn=0.080299,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis server enjoys drinking coffee, gazing at Mount Rainier, and riding ferryboats.  ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Seattle, à Washington et offre une bonne option pour tester les applications dans l’Ouest Américaine et en Asie-Pacifique.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=seattle&amp;sll=37.351601,-121.924896&amp;sspn=0.176577,0.264702&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ll=47.620975,-122.34478&amp;spn=0.080299,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=seattle&amp;sll=37.351601,-121.924896&amp;sspn=0.176577,0.264702&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ll=47.620975,-122.34478&amp;spn=0.080299,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime boire le café, visiter le Mont Ranier, et utiliser les navettes fluviales.\n'), ('25', 'Tallinn', 'Estonia', 'This server is located in Tallinn, Estonia. <br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tallinn,+Estonia&amp;sll=47.601765,-122.331734&amp;sspn=0.149777,0.264702&amp;g=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Tallinn,+Harjumaa,+Estonia&amp;ll=61.856149,14.414063&amp;spn=14.468736,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tallinn,+Estonia&amp;sll=47.601765,-122.331734&amp;sspn=0.149777,0.264702&amp;g=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Tallinn,+Harjumaa,+Estonia&amp;ll=61.856149,14.414063&amp;spn=14.468736,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis server spends its days visiting the many meteorite craters that dot the Estonian landscape.  It delights in misrouting anyone that misidentifies it as Latvian or Lithuanian.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Tallinn, en Estonie.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tallinn,+Estonia&amp;sll=47.601765,-122.331734&amp;sspn=0.149777,0.264702&amp;g=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Tallinn,+Harjumaa,+Estonia&amp;ll=61.856149,14.414063&amp;spn=14.468736,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Tallinn,+Estonia&amp;sll=47.601765,-122.331734&amp;sspn=0.149777,0.264702&amp;g=Seattle,+King,+Washington&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Tallinn,+Harjumaa,+Estonia&amp;ll=61.856149,14.414063&amp;spn=14.468736,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nCe serveur aime visiter les cratères de météorite autour du pays (il y a beaucoup).  Il aime mal-diriger les données de ceux qui pense qu’il est Latvien ou Lithuanien.'), ('26', 'Copenhagen', 'Denmark', 'This server is located in Copenhagen, Denmark and is an excellent option for testing your GeoIP applications in this smallest Scandinavian country. <br><br>\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;sll=59.451707,24.715118&amp;sspn=0.2258,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;ll=58.401712,7.294922&amp;spn=16.052692,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;sll=59.451707,24.715118&amp;sspn=0.2258,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;ll=58.401712,7.294922&amp;spn=16.052692,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis server wishes its users to know that Copenhagen has the two oldest amusement parks in the world - when not doing its thing, it enjoys playing ice hockey, handball, and sampling the local beer.  It is especially happy when people spell its name right: København.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Copenhague, au Danemark.  Il est une excellente option pour tester vos applications GeoIP dans le plus petit pays de la Scandinavie.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;sll=59.451707,24.715118&amp;sspn=0.2258,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;ll=58.401712,7.294922&amp;spn=16.052692,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;sll=59.451707,24.715118&amp;sspn=0.2258,0.529404&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Copenhagen,+Denmark&amp;ll=58.401712,7.294922&amp;spn=16.052692,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur veut que ses utilisateurs soient conscients que deux des plus anciens parcs d’amusement au monde sont à Copenhague.  Lorsqu’il ne dirige pas les données, il passe le temps à jouer à l’hockey et le handball, ou à la dégustation de la bière locale.  Il est particulièrement heureux quand les gens épèlent son nom correctement : København.\n'), ('27', 'Milan', 'Italy', 'This sever is located in Milan, Italy.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=v.+Caldera,+21+20123,+Milano&amp;sll=45.475856,9.093289&amp;sspn=0.009735,0.016544&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Via+Caldera,+21,+20153+Milano,+Lombardia,+Italy&amp;ll=47.754098,6.723633&amp;spn=10.252055,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=v.+Caldera,+21+20123,+Milano&amp;sll=45.475856,9.093289&amp;sspn=0.009735,0.016544&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Via+Caldera,+21,+20153+Milano,+Lombardia,+Italy&amp;ll=47.754098,6.723633&amp;spn=10.252055,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nWhen not eating cassouela or ossobuco, this server enjoys window shopping, attempting to find the perfect pair of designer shoes to go with its casing, and heckling A.C. Milan fans.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Milan, en Italie.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=v.+Caldera,+21+20123,+Milano&amp;sll=45.475856,9.093289&amp;sspn=0.009735,0.016544&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Via+Caldera,+21,+20153+Milano,+Lombardia,+Italy&amp;ll=47.754098,6.723633&amp;spn=10.252055,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=v.+Caldera,+21+20123,+Milano&amp;sll=45.475856,9.093289&amp;sspn=0.009735,0.016544&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Via+Caldera,+21,+20153+Milano,+Lombardia,+Italy&amp;ll=47.754098,6.723633&amp;spn=10.252055,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nLorsqu’il ne mange pas, ce serveur aime faire du lèche-vitrine, chercher les souliers parfaites pour matcher son boîtier et se moquer des partisans d’A.C. Milan.'), ('28', 'Bucharest', 'Romania', 'This server is located in Bucharest, Romania!  Romania is considered by many credit card processing agencies to be a high risk country for fraud - this proxy provides an excellent place to test that element of your code base, as well as elements using GeoIP. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=44.430593,26.096649&amp;sspn=0.069137,0.219212&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.667628,21.533203&amp;spn=19.945707,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=44.430593,26.096649&amp;sspn=0.069137,0.219212&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.667628,21.533203&amp;spn=19.945707,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not routing your traffic and helping you test your GeoIP applications, this server enjoys giving tourists bad directions to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bran_Castle\">Bran Castle</a> and windsurfing on Morii Lake.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Bucharest en Roumanie.  La Roumanie est considérée par beaucoup de compagnies de traitement de carte de crédit d’être un région d’haute risque de fraude; ce serveur vous offre une bonne opportunité de tester ce partie de votre code, et les applications GeoIP. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=44.430593,26.096649&amp;sspn=0.069137,0.219212&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.667628,21.533203&amp;spn=19.945707,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=44.430593,26.096649&amp;sspn=0.069137,0.219212&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bucharest,+Bucuresti,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.667628,21.533203&amp;spn=19.945707,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nLorsqu\'il n\'est pas en train de diriger vos données ou de vous aider à tester vos applications GeoIP, ce serveur aime mal-diriger les touristes qui cherchent <a href=\"http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ch%C3%A2teau_de_Bran\">le château de Bran</a> et faire du planche à voile sur le lac Morii.');
INSERT INTO `servers_details` VALUES ('29', 'Frankfurt', 'Germany', 'This server is located in Frankfurt, Germany.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=frankfurt+germany&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Frankfurt,+Frankfurt+am+Main,+Hesse,+Germany&amp;ll=51.645294,8.349609&amp;spn=9.465955,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=frankfurt+germany&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Frankfurt,+Frankfurt+am+Main,+Hesse,+Germany&amp;ll=51.645294,8.349609&amp;spn=9.465955,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis server enjoys long walks along the Rhine, visiting Frankfurt\'s food markets, and perfecting its schnitzel recipes.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Francfort, en Allemagne.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=frankfurt+germany&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Frankfurt,+Frankfurt+am+Main,+Hesse,+Germany&amp;ll=51.645294,8.349609&amp;spn=9.465955,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=frankfurt+germany&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Frankfurt,+Frankfurt+am+Main,+Hesse,+Germany&amp;ll=51.645294,8.349609&amp;spn=9.465955,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime se promener le long du Rhin, visiter les marchés publics de Francfort, et perfectionner ses recettes de Schnitzel.\n\n'), ('30', 'Fremont', 'United States', 'This server is in a first class data center in Fremont, California. Fremont holds servers for many of the most popular web destinations, as well as trendy up and coming web 2.0 properties. WonderProxy is able to provide great data rates on this server, and is happy to handle any special requests here.\n<br /><br />\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Fremont,+California&amp;sll=37.54827,-121.988572&amp;sspn=0.230825,0.339546&amp;g=Freemont,+California&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Fremont,+Alameda,+California&amp;ll=37.641422,-122.091064&amp;spn=0.380603,0.858307&amp;z=10&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Fremont,+California&amp;sll=37.54827,-121.988572&amp;sspn=0.230825,0.339546&amp;g=Freemont,+California&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Fremont,+Alameda,+California&amp;ll=37.641422,-122.091064&amp;spn=0.380603,0.858307&amp;z=10&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\n<br /><br />\nThis server\'s passtimes include mocking the young and too gainfully employed for their silly wardrobe, trendy but empty moleskin notebooks, and anyone on a scooter.\n', null), ('31', 'Singapore', 'Republic of Singapore', 'This server resides in Singapore, Singapore!<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=singapore+city,+singapore&amp;sll=50.805935,9.755859&amp;sspn=8.987235,16.940918&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Singapore&amp;ll=2.086941,102.854004&amp;spn=3.809013,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=singapore+city,+singapore&amp;sll=50.805935,9.755859&amp;sspn=8.987235,16.940918&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Singapore&amp;ll=2.086941,102.854004&amp;spn=3.809013,6.866455&amp;z=7\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis server lives on the island of Singapore.  When not avoiding the rains of the monsoon season, it enjoys exploring the rainforest and keeping its /temp fastidiously clean.  Singapore offers a second option for testing GeoIP applications targetted at Asia-Pacific, alongside our Malaysian server.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Singapore, au Singapore!\n\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=singapore+city,+singapore&amp;sll=50.805935,9.755859&amp;sspn=8.987235,16.940918&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Singapore&amp;ll=2.086941,102.854004&amp;spn=3.809013,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=singapore+city,+singapore&amp;sll=50.805935,9.755859&amp;sspn=8.987235,16.940918&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Singapore&amp;ll=2.086941,102.854004&amp;spn=3.809013,6.866455&amp;z=7\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur vit sur l’île du Singapore.  Lorsqu’il ne se cache pas des pluies de la mousson, il aime explorer la forêt tropicale et fastitieusement nettoyer son /temp.  Singapore est parmis nos options pour tester les applications GeoIP en Asie-Pacifique, avec Malaysie et l’Indonésie.\n'), ('32', 'Warsaw', 'Poland', 'This server is located in Warsaw, Poland.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=warsaw,+poland&amp;aq=&amp;sll=53.748711,16.743164&amp;sspn=14.689695,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Warsaw,+Warszawa,+Masovian+Voivodeship,+Poland&amp;t=m&amp;ll=54.699234,17.490234&amp;spn=8.896907,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=warsaw,+poland&amp;aq=&amp;sll=53.748711,16.743164&amp;sspn=14.689695,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Warsaw,+Warszawa,+Masovian+Voivodeship,+Poland&amp;t=m&amp;ll=54.699234,17.490234&amp;spn=8.896907,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nRumour has it that when not perfecting its polka, this server enjoys travelling and snowsports.  Its technicians appears to speak exclusively Polish, however, so these rumours remain unconfirmed.', 'Ce server se situe à Varsovie en Pologne.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Warsaw,+Poland&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=54.059388,16.743164&amp;sspn=13.958826,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Varsovie,+Warszawa,+Vo%C3%AFvodie+de+Mazovie,+Pologne&amp;t=m&amp;ll=54.572062,19.072266&amp;spn=8.924662,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Warsaw,+Poland&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=54.059388,16.743164&amp;sspn=13.958826,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Varsovie,+Warszawa,+Vo%C3%AFvodie+de+Mazovie,+Pologne&amp;t=m&amp;ll=54.572062,19.072266&amp;spn=8.924662,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nLa rumeur dit que lorsqu’il n’est pas en train de perfectionner son polka, il aime faire du ski et du planche a neige… comme ses techniciens ne parlent que du polonais, nous ne pouvons ni confirmer ni infirmer ces rumeurs.\n'), ('33', 'Mexico', 'Mexico', 'This server is located in Mexico City, Mexico. It provides our Mexican point of presence. It is one of our more expensive hosts as most providers in that country choose to physically locate their servers in the Southern United States (for great rates and connectivity).\n<br /><br />\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=mexico+city,+mexico&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=58.164117,86.923828&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Mexico+City,+Distrito+Federal,+Mexico&amp;ll=19.491839,-99.183884&amp;spn=0.226552,0.429153&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=mexico+city,+mexico&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=58.164117,86.923828&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Mexico+City,+Distrito+Federal,+Mexico&amp;ll=19.491839,-99.183884&amp;spn=0.226552,0.429153&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\n<br /><br />\nThis server\'s pastimes include patiently explaining to tourists that Taco Bell is in fact not \"authentic mexican cuisine\" as they insist. But does admit to eating at chipotle on occasion. ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Mexico City, au Mexique, et fournit notre présence Mexicaine.  Il est parmi les serveurs les plus dispendieux de notre réseau, puissque la majorité de fournisseurs web du pays se servent des serveurs davantage abordables et fiables dans le Sud des États-Unis.\n\n<br /><br />\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=mexico+city,+mexico&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=58.164117,86.923828&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Mexico+City,+Distrito+Federal,+Mexico&amp;ll=19.491839,-99.183884&amp;spn=0.226552,0.429153&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=mexico+city,+mexico&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=58.164117,86.923828&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Mexico+City,+Distrito+Federal,+Mexico&amp;ll=19.491839,-99.183884&amp;spn=0.226552,0.429153&amp;z=11&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br /><br />\n\n\nSes passe-temps incluent expliquer aux touristes que Taco Bell n’est pas la cuisine Mexicaine authentique, mais il doit admettre qu’il mange à Chipotle de temps en temps.\n'), ('34', 'Kiev', 'Ukraine', 'This server is located in Kiev, Ukraine.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&amp;q=kiev,+ukraine&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kiev,+Kyiv,+Ukraine&amp;ll=53.592505,19.160156&amp;spn=18.151135,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&amp;q=kiev,+ukraine&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kiev,+Kyiv,+Ukraine&amp;ll=53.592505,19.160156&amp;spn=18.151135,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis server boasts to all and sundry that it has won its datacenter\'s chicken kiev cookoff three years in a row.  It has been asking the Warsaw server to dance since it they shared a love of the polka.  Sadly, so far it has had been met with uncharacteristic silence.', 'Ce serveur se situe en Kiev, en Ukraine.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=fr&amp;q=kiev,+ukraine&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kiev,+Kyiv,+Ukraine&amp;ll=53.592505,19.160156&amp;spn=18.151135,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=fr&amp;q=kiev,+ukraine&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kiev,+Kyiv,+Ukraine&amp;ll=53.592505,19.160156&amp;spn=18.151135,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nCe serveur se vente d’avoir été gagnant du compétition de poulet à la Kiev de son centre de données trois années de suite.  Depuis sa découverte que notre serveur à Varsovie aime le polka, il le demande à danser, mais n’a pas reçu de réponse.'), ('35', 'Zurich', 'Switzerland', 'This server is located in Zurich, Switzerland.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Zurich,+Switzerland&amp;sll=49.095452,24.213867&amp;sspn=18.637766,33.881836&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Z%C3%BCrich+District,+Z%C3%BCrich,+Canton+of+Z%C3%BCrich,+Switzerland&amp;ll=48.297812,6.481934&amp;spn=5.071976,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Zurich,+Switzerland&amp;sll=49.095452,24.213867&amp;sspn=18.637766,33.881836&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Z%C3%BCrich+District,+Z%C3%BCrich,+Canton+of+Z%C3%BCrich,+Switzerland&amp;ll=48.297812,6.481934&amp;spn=5.071976,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nThis server enjoys swimming in Lake Zurich, visiting the Swiss National Museum, and listening to Wagner.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Zurich, en Suisse.\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Zurich,+Switzerland&amp;sll=49.095452,24.213867&amp;sspn=18.637766,33.881836&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Z%C3%BCrich+District,+Z%C3%BCrich,+Canton+of+Z%C3%BCrich,+Switzerland&amp;ll=48.297812,6.481934&amp;spn=5.071976,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Zurich,+Switzerland&amp;sll=49.095452,24.213867&amp;sspn=18.637766,33.881836&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Z%C3%BCrich+District,+Z%C3%BCrich,+Canton+of+Z%C3%BCrich,+Switzerland&amp;ll=48.297812,6.481934&amp;spn=5.071976,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nCe serveur aime nager dans le Lac Zurich, visiter la Musée nationale de la Suisse, et écouter du Wagner.  Il aime également dire au serveur Montréalais que son accent est mignon.\n'), ('36', 'Malaysia', 'Malaysia', 'This server is located in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Wilayah+Persekutuan+Kuala+Lumpur+Malaysia&amp;sll=3.139145,101.686707&amp;sspn=0.887177,1.058807&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Federal+Territory+of+Kuala+Lumpur,+Malaysia&amp;ll=8.233237,94.570313&amp;spn=29.84435,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Wilayah+Persekutuan+Kuala+Lumpur+Malaysia&amp;sll=3.139145,101.686707&amp;sspn=0.887177,1.058807&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Federal+Territory+of+Kuala+Lumpur,+Malaysia&amp;ll=8.233237,94.570313&amp;spn=29.84435,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\nWhen not providing access to Asia Pacific, this server enjoys travelling into the Malaysian jungle while carefully avoiding leeches, and eating noodles. ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Kuala Lumpur, en Malaysie.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Wilayah+Persekutuan+Kuala+Lumpur+Malaysia&amp;sll=3.139145,101.686707&amp;sspn=0.887177,1.058807&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Federal+Territory+of+Kuala+Lumpur,+Malaysia&amp;ll=8.233237,94.570313&amp;spn=29.84435,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Wilayah+Persekutuan+Kuala+Lumpur+Malaysia&amp;sll=3.139145,101.686707&amp;sspn=0.887177,1.058807&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Federal+Territory+of+Kuala+Lumpur,+Malaysia&amp;ll=8.233237,94.570313&amp;spn=29.84435,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\nLorsqu’il n’offre pas accès à l’Asie-Pacifique, ce serveur aime voyager dans le jungle (tout en évitant les sangsues) et manger des nouilles. \n'), ('37', 'Los Angeles', 'United States', 'This server is located in Los Angeles, California, USA.  With a population of 3.8million, Los Angeles is the second most populous city in the United States: if you care about city-by-city performance, this server is for you!<br><br>  \n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Los+Angeles,+CA,+United+States&amp;aq=&amp;sll=34.05014,-118.250354&amp;sspn=0.009512,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Los+Angeles,+California,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,-117.46582&amp;spn=3.153996,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Los+Angeles,+CA,+United+States&amp;aq=&amp;sll=34.05014,-118.250354&amp;sspn=0.009512,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Los+Angeles,+California,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,-117.46582&amp;spn=3.153996,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server also enjoys giving bad directions to Hollywood, and hopes one day to forward Angelina Jolie\'s email.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Los Angèle, à Californie, aux États-Unis.  Avec un population de 3,8millions de personnes, Los Angèle est la deuxième ville des États-Unis, et si vous désirez tester par ville, ce serveur est une bonne choix.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Los+Angeles,+CA,+United+States&amp;aq=&amp;sll=34.05014,-118.250354&amp;sspn=0.009512,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Los+Angeles,+California,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,-117.46582&amp;spn=3.153996,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Los+Angeles,+CA,+United+States&amp;aq=&amp;sll=34.05014,-118.250354&amp;sspn=0.009512,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Los+Angeles,+California,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,-117.46582&amp;spn=3.153996,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime mal-diriger les touristes qui cherchent l’Hollywood, et espère un jour diriger les courriels d’Angelina Jolie.\n'), ('38', 'Phoenix', 'United States', 'This server is located in Phoenix, Arizona.  Is your GeoIP-using application working correctly?  Here\'s an opportunity to check whether it appropriately locates Phoenix as an area that does not observe daylight saving\'s time!<br><br> \n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Phoenix,+AZ,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=34.759666,-117.883301&amp;sspn=4.827812,9.876709&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Phoenix,+Maricopa,+Arizona,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.029996,-112.895508&amp;spn=6.295707,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Phoenix,+AZ,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=34.759666,-117.883301&amp;sspn=4.827812,9.876709&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Phoenix,+Maricopa,+Arizona,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.029996,-112.895508&amp;spn=6.295707,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nOn its days off, this server enjoys visiting freezers to avoid the blistering heat, and dreaming of snow.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Phoenix, en Arizona.  Est-ce que votre application GeoIP opère comme prévu?  Voici une option pour vérifier s’il identifie correctement que Phoenix n’observe pas les heures avancés d’été!<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Phoenix,+AZ,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=34.759666,-117.883301&amp;sspn=4.827812,9.876709&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Phoenix,+Maricopa,+Arizona,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.029996,-112.895508&amp;spn=6.295707,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Phoenix,+AZ,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=34.759666,-117.883301&amp;sspn=4.827812,9.876709&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Phoenix,+Maricopa,+Arizona,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.029996,-112.895508&amp;spn=6.295707,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\n\nEn pause, ce serveur aime visiter les congélateurs pour éviter la chaleur, et rêver de la neige.'), ('39', 'Houston', 'United States', 'This server is located in Houston, Texas.  It prides itself on being a star server servicing the fourth-largest city in the United States and is a great option for testing GeoIP applications in the US South. <br><br>\n\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Houston,+TX,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=59.701014,22.434082&amp;sspn=5.934842,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Houston,+Harris,+Texas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=33.211116,-97.822266&amp;spn=12.853022,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Houston,+TX,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=59.701014,22.434082&amp;sspn=5.934842,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Houston,+Harris,+Texas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=33.211116,-97.822266&amp;spn=12.853022,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><Br>\n\nWhen idle, this server enjoys solving virtual Rubix cubes, and challenging its friends to Minesweeper competitions.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Houston, au Texas.  Il est fier d’être un serveur vedette au service de la quatrième ville des États-Unis, et d’être une excellente option pour le testing d’applications GeoIP dans le Sud Américaine.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Houston,+TX,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=59.701014,22.434082&amp;sspn=5.934842,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Houston,+Harris,+Texas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=33.211116,-97.822266&amp;spn=12.853022,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Houston,+TX,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=59.701014,22.434082&amp;sspn=5.934842,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Houston,+Harris,+Texas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=33.211116,-97.822266&amp;spn=12.853022,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><Br>\n\n\nEn repos, ce serveur aime jouer avec des cube rubik vituelles, et inviter ses amis à des compétitions de Minesweeper.\n'), ('40', 'Baltimore', 'United States', 'This server is located in Baltimore, Maryland, making it a great choice for testing GeoIP-sensitive applications on the US East Coast. <br><br> \n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Baltimore,+MD,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=38.89906,-77.04773&amp;sspn=1.14355,2.469177&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Baltimore,+Maryland,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=39.29731,-76.614447&amp;spn=0.023248,0.053644&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Baltimore,+MD,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=38.89906,-77.04773&amp;sspn=1.14355,2.469177&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Baltimore,+Maryland,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=39.29731,-76.614447&amp;spn=0.023248,0.053644&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not routing data, it enjoys staring out at Chesapeake Bay, and attending baseball games. \n', 'Ce serveur se situe à Baltimore, au Maryland, et est une bonne option pour tester les applications GeoIP dans l’Est Américaine.\r<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Baltimore,+Maryland,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=33.742613,-84.375&amp;sspn=9.913317,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Baltimore,+Maryland,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=40.069665,-76.860352&amp;spn=2.942503,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Baltimore,+Maryland,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=33.742613,-84.375&amp;sspn=9.913317,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Baltimore,+Maryland,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=40.069665,-76.860352&amp;spn=2.942503,6.866455&amp;z=7&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\rLorsqu’il ne dirige pas vos données, il aime contempler la baie Chesapeake, et assister aux jeux de baseball.\r'), ('41', 'London2', 'United Kingdom', 'This location provides our second point of presence in London, it was acquired to provide a greater variety of IP addresses than our original host could provide.\n', null), ('42', 'Cape Town', 'South Africa', ' This server is located in Cape Town, South Africa. It was our first location on the African continent and rounds out our coverage alongside Egypt and Morocco.  It\'s a great testing location for people targeting South African customers. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.293989,-76.61376&amp;sspn=0.035537,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-33.898917,18.459435&amp;spn=0.099738,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.293989,-76.61376&amp;sspn=0.035537,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-33.898917,18.459435&amp;spn=0.099738,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server\'s pass-times include managing a world-cup trading pool and playing football with other servers nearby when the sys-admin isn\'t looking.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Cape Town en Afrique du Sud.  Il était notre premier serveur en Afrique, et complète notre réseau Africaine, avec nos serveurs à Maroc et en Égypte.  Il est une option idéale pour ceux qui veulent tester des applications ciblé aux clients Sud-Africaines.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.293989,-76.61376&amp;sspn=0.035537,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-33.898917,18.459435&amp;spn=0.099738,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.293989,-76.61376&amp;sspn=0.035537,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cape+Town,+Western+Cape,+South+Africa&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-33.898917,18.459435&amp;spn=0.099738,0.214577&amp;z=12&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nSes passe-temps incluent la gestion d’une ligue de Fantasy Football pour la coupe mondiale, et jouer au soccer avec les autres serveurs quand son sys-admin a le dos tourné.'), ('43', 'Bruges', 'Belgium', 'This server is located in Brussels, Belgium.  It is a great choice of server if you want to check that your application correctly handles GeoIP issues in this bilingual (Duth and French) city.<br><br><iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brussels,+Belgium&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=City+of+Brussels,+Brussels,+Belgium&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.038977,3.164063&amp;spn=4.731439,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brussels,+Belgium&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=City+of+Brussels,+Brussels,+Belgium&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.038977,3.164063&amp;spn=4.731439,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n This server enjoys sampling the varied architecture of Brussels, not to mention its beer.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Bruxelles, en Belgique.  Il est une bonne option pour vérifier que votre application gère le GeoIP dans cette ville bilingue (néerlandais et français).\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brussels,+Belgium&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=City+of+Brussels,+Brussels,+Belgium&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.038977,3.164063&amp;spn=4.731439,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Brussels,+Belgium&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=City+of+Brussels,+Brussels,+Belgium&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.038977,3.164063&amp;spn=4.731439,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nCe serveur aime étudier l’architecture variée de Bruxelles, ainsi que sa bière.'), ('44', 'Lisbon', 'Portugal', 'This server is located in Lisbon, Portugal.  If you\'re testing GeoIP applications targeting Europe, this server can help you check that your Portuguese is displaying properly.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-43.548548,172.661133&amp;sspn=18.437871,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.032974,-11.162109&amp;spn=11.420651,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-43.548548,172.661133&amp;sspn=18.437871,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.032974,-11.162109&amp;spn=11.420651,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys reminding our servers in London, Paris and Rome that Lisbon was founded hundreds of years before they were, chatting with our Brazilian server, and cooking delicious foodstuffs.  \r\n', 'Ce serveur se situe à Lisbonne, au Portugal.  Si vous testez des applications GeoIP ciblé à l’Europe, ce serveur peut vérifier que votre Portugaise est correcte.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-43.548548,172.661133&amp;sspn=18.437871,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.032974,-11.162109&amp;spn=11.420651,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-43.548548,172.661133&amp;sspn=18.437871,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Lisbon,+Portugal&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.032974,-11.162109&amp;spn=11.420651,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime faire souvenir à nos serveurs à Londres, Paris et Rome que Lisbonne était fondée des centaines d’années avant eux, bavarder avec notre serveur au Brésil, et cuire des mets délicieuses.\n'), ('45', 'Helsinki', 'Finland', 'This server is situated in Helsinki Finland.  It enjoys waving across the sea at our servers in Tallinn and Stockholm while providing excellent coverage for Finnish geotesting.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=CcEMQMoiCtgUFRGGVwIdo_1u-ym3g_TWrgPIiTFY5yNCqJZIBA&amp;q=Helsinki+Finland&amp;aq=&amp;sll=39.282626,-76.630772&amp;sspn=0.071086,0.154324&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Helsinki,+Finland&amp;t=m&amp;ll=61.980267,20.742188&amp;spn=7.237629,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=CcEMQMoiCtgUFRGGVwIdo_1u-ym3g_TWrgPIiTFY5yNCqJZIBA&amp;q=Helsinki+Finland&amp;aq=&amp;sll=39.282626,-76.630772&amp;sspn=0.071086,0.154324&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Helsinki,+Finland&amp;t=m&amp;ll=61.980267,20.742188&amp;spn=7.237629,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not helping people test their Geo-IP sensitive applications\' performance in Scandinavia, it enjoys listening to Apocalyptica and maintaining its Linus Torvalds fansite. ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Helsinki, en Finlande.  Il aime saluer ses collègues à Tallin et Stockholm de la main, tout en fournissant une option pour le testing GeoIP en Finlande.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=CcEMQMoiCtgUFRGGVwIdo_1u-ym3g_TWrgPIiTFY5yNCqJZIBA&amp;q=Helsinki+Finland&amp;aq=&amp;sll=39.282626,-76.630772&amp;sspn=0.071086,0.154324&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Helsinki,+Finland&amp;t=m&amp;ll=61.980267,20.742188&amp;spn=7.237629,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=CcEMQMoiCtgUFRGGVwIdo_1u-ym3g_TWrgPIiTFY5yNCqJZIBA&amp;q=Helsinki+Finland&amp;aq=&amp;sll=39.282626,-76.630772&amp;sspn=0.071086,0.154324&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Helsinki,+Finland&amp;t=m&amp;ll=61.980267,20.742188&amp;spn=7.237629,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\nLorsqu’il n’aide pas les gens à tester la performance de leurs applications GeoIP en Scandinavie, il aime écouter la musique d’Apocalyptica et mettre à jour son fansite de Linus Torvalds.'), ('46', 'New Delhi', 'India', 'This server is located in New Delhi, India.  We\'re excited to offer an Indian option for developers to test Geo-IP sensitive applications in the world\'s second-most populous country.  This server in particular is ideal for application testing in Northern India. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=new+delhi&amp;aq=&amp;sll=43.673801,-79.455764&amp;sspn=0.008303,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=New+Delhi,+Delhi,+India&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.38905,75.498047&amp;spn=24.97721,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=new+delhi&amp;aq=&amp;sll=43.673801,-79.455764&amp;sspn=0.008303,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=New+Delhi,+Delhi,+India&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.38905,75.498047&amp;spn=24.97721,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not routing data, this server enjoys guessing the temperature in far-off countries while watching the evening news, and sampling the culinary delights offered by New Delhi\'s many street vendors.  ', 'Ce serveur se situe à New Delhi, en Inde.  Nous sommes très contents d’offrir une option en Inde pour les programmeurs qui veulent tester leurs applications GeoIP dans la deuxième plus important pays (par population) au monde.  Ce serveur est particulièrement utile pour tester les applications dans le Nord de l’Inde.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=new+delhi&amp;aq=&amp;sll=43.673801,-79.455764&amp;sspn=0.008303,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=New+Delhi,+Delhi,+India&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.38905,75.498047&amp;spn=24.97721,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=new+delhi&amp;aq=&amp;sll=43.673801,-79.455764&amp;sspn=0.008303,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=New+Delhi,+Delhi,+India&amp;t=m&amp;ll=35.38905,75.498047&amp;spn=24.97721,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nLorsqu’il ne dirige pas les données, ce serveur aime deviner la température des pays distantes quand il écoute les nouvelles, et manger les mets offerts par la panoplie des stands de nourriture de New Delhi.'), ('47', 'Budapest', 'Hungary', 'This server is located in Budapest, Hungary.  This is server provides additional coverage in Eastern Europe, and is a great option for testing your GeoIP applications in an area with a high perceived level of risk, .   <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=30.069094,31.26709&amp;sspn=10.163494,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.233152,16.21582&amp;spn=9.843881,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=30.069094,31.26709&amp;sspn=10.163494,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.233152,16.21582&amp;spn=9.843881,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThe Romans initially colonized the region that would become Budapest because of its rich thermal springs: when not routing your data, this server particularly enjoys visiting the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sz%C3%A9chenyi_Baths\">Széchenyi Baths</a>, the largest medicinal bath in Europe.\n', 'Ce serveur est situé à Budapest, en Hongrie.  Il fournit d’autres options dans l’Europe Orientale, et est une bonne option pour vérifier vos applications GeoIP dans une région avec un niveau de risque perçu élevé.<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=30.069094,31.26709&amp;sspn=10.163494,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.233152,16.21582&amp;spn=9.843881,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=30.069094,31.26709&amp;sspn=10.163494,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.233152,16.21582&amp;spn=9.843881,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\nLe romains ont colonisé la région devenue Budapest à cause de ses sources thermiques : lorsqu’il est en pause de diriger vos données, ce serveur aime visiter les bains Széchenyi, la plus grande bain médicinal de l’Europe.'), ('48', 'Bergen', 'Norway', 'Bergen, a beautiful city nestled between the coast and the mountains experiences a bountiful rainfall every year (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bergen#Climate\">85 consecutive days</a> of rain 2006-2007), making it a perfect location to test not only your Norwegian GeoIP-targetting applications, but also a great place to market wet weather gear.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=bergen,+norway&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bergen,+Hordaland,+Norway&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=64.052978,0.703125&amp;spn=13.558097,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=bergen,+norway&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bergen,+Hordaland,+Norway&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=64.052978,0.703125&amp;spn=13.558097,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys toying with fractals to generate fjords, re-purposing old umbrella dispensing machines, and planning the Norway in a Nutshell tour.', 'Bergen, une magnifique ville située entre l’eau et les montagnes, reçoit une quantité impressionnante de pluie chaque année (<a href=\"http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bergen_(Norv%C3%A8ge)#Climat\">85 jours consécutives de pluie</a> en 2006-2007).  Il est donc une ville parfaite pour tester les applications GeoIP en Norvège, en plus d’être idéalement située pour le markéting des vêtements de pluie.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=bergen,+norway&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bergen,+Hordaland,+Norway&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=64.052978,0.703125&amp;spn=13.558097,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=bergen,+norway&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bergen,+Hordaland,+Norway&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=64.052978,0.703125&amp;spn=13.558097,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime jouer avec les fractales pour créer des fjords, modifier les veilles machines-distributrices de parapluie pour créer des sculptures, et planifier l’excursion <a href=\"http://www.norwaynutshell.com/\">‘Norway in a Nutshell’</a>.'), ('49', 'Medellin', 'Colombia', 'This server is located in Medellin, Colombia.  When not directing traffic, it designs flower arrangements for the annual Colombian Festival of the Flowers.  It provides extra coverage for testing GeoIP sensitive applications in South America, along with our servers in Argentina and Brazil.<br><br> <iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=medellin+colombia&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Medell%C3%ADn,+Antioquia,+Colombia&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=13.923404,-77.958984&amp;spn=29.545213,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=medellin+colombia&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Medell%C3%ADn,+Antioquia,+Colombia&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=13.923404,-77.958984&amp;spn=29.545213,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>  ', 'données, il aime créer des sculptures florales pour le festival annuel de fleurs de la Colombie.  Il fournit un autre option pour tester les applications GeoIP en Amérique-du-Sud, avec nos serveurs en Argentin et au Brésil.\n\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=medellin+colombia&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=fr&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Medell%C3%ADn,+Antioquia,+Colombia&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=13.923404,-77.958984&amp;spn=29.545213,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=medellin+colombia&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=fr&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Medell%C3%ADn,+Antioquia,+Colombia&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=13.923404,-77.958984&amp;spn=29.545213,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>  '), ('50', 'Rosario', 'Argentina', 'This server is located in Rosario, Argentina, 300km northwest of Buenos Aires.  It\'s one of our great options for testing GeoIP-using applications in South America, along with Medellin and Brazil.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?hl=en&amp;q=rosario+argentina+map&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rosario,+Santa+Fe+Province,+Argentina&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=-29.53523,-58.623047&amp;spn=13.361493,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?hl=en&amp;q=rosario+argentina+map&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rosario,+Santa+Fe+Province,+Argentina&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=-29.53523,-58.623047&amp;spn=13.361493,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nOn its days off it enjoys sunning itself in the parks that border the Paraná river, and visiting the Experimental Science Museum.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Rosario, en Argentin, 300km au Nord-Ouest de Buenos Aires.  Il est une excellente option pour tester les applications GeoIP en Amérique du Sud, avec Medellin et Brésil.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?hl=fr&amp;q=rosario+argentina+map&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rosario,+Santa+Fe+Province,+Argentina&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=-29.53523,-58.623047&amp;spn=13.361493,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?hl=fr&amp;q=rosario+argentina+map&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rosario,+Santa+Fe+Province,+Argentina&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=-29.53523,-58.623047&amp;spn=13.361493,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nLes jours de congés, il aime marcher le longue de la rivière Paraná et visiter le musée de science expérimentale.\n'), ('51', 'San Antonio', 'United States', 'This server is located in San Antonio, Texas.  WonderProxy overs excellent coverage for developers testing GeoIP applications in Texas, with additional severs in Dallas and Houston. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=san+antonio+texas&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=San+Antonio,+Bexar,+Texas,+United+States&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=31.222197,-98.613281&amp;spn=6.57429,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=san+antonio+texas&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=San+Antonio,+Bexar,+Texas,+United+States&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=31.222197,-98.613281&amp;spn=6.57429,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not routing your data, this server enjoys watching attending San Antonio Spurs games, inviting friends over to cool off in the server rooms, and going for long car rides in search of tumbleweeds.', 'Ce serveur se situe à San Antonio, au Texas.  WonderProxy offre une vaste réseau aux programmeurs qui veulent tester les applications GeoIP au Texas, avec des serveurs à San Antonio, Dallas, et Houston.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=san+antonio+texas&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=San+Antonio,+Bexar,+Texas,+United+States&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=31.222197,-98.613281&amp;spn=6.57429,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=san+antonio+texas&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=San+Antonio,+Bexar,+Texas,+United+States&amp;gl=ca&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=31.222197,-98.613281&amp;spn=6.57429,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\nLorsqu’il ne dirige pas vos données, ce serveur aime écouter les matches des San Antonio Spurs, inviter ses amis à son chambre de serveur pour qu’ils déchauffent, et prendre des longues voyages en voiture pour voir les ‘Tumbleweed’.'), ('52', 'Montreal', 'Canada', 'This server is located in beautiful Montréal, Canada, the birthplace of WonderProxy!  It\'s a great option to check that your Geo-IP sensitive application is appearing correctly to both English and French-speaking Canadians.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Guy+and+Sainte-Catherine&amp;aq=&amp;sll=45.49997,-73.571577&amp;sspn=0.032185,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rue+Guy+%26+Sainte-Catherine+St+W,+Montr%C3%A9al,+Communaut%C3%A9-Urbaine-de-Montr%C3%A9al,+Qu%C3%A9bec&amp;t=m&amp;ll=45.498406,-73.582821&amp;spn=0.042113,0.107288&amp;z=13&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Guy+and+Sainte-Catherine&amp;aq=&amp;sll=45.49997,-73.571577&amp;sspn=0.032185,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rue+Guy+%26+Sainte-Catherine+St+W,+Montr%C3%A9al,+Communaut%C3%A9-Urbaine-de-Montr%C3%A9al,+Qu%C3%A9bec&amp;t=m&amp;ll=45.498406,-73.582821&amp;spn=0.042113,0.107288&amp;z=13\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nIt enjoys cycling, baking, bilingualism, and visiting the \'world famous\' Lachine Rapids.  It hates it when people pronounce Montréal as MAWN-TREE-all.', 'Ce serveur se situe dans la magnifique ville de Montréal, ville natale de WonderProxy!  C’est une excellente option pour vérifier que vos applications apparaît correctement pour vos clients Francophones et Angolophones.\n<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Guy+and+Sainte-Catherine&amp;aq=&amp;sll=45.49997,-73.571577&amp;sspn=0.032185,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rue+Guy+%26+Sainte-Catherine+St+W,+Montr%C3%A9al,+Communaut%C3%A9-Urbaine-de-Montr%C3%A9al,+Qu%C3%A9bec&amp;t=m&amp;ll=45.498406,-73.582821&amp;spn=0.042113,0.107288&amp;z=13&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Guy+and+Sainte-Catherine&amp;aq=&amp;sll=45.49997,-73.571577&amp;sspn=0.032185,0.077162&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Rue+Guy+%26+Sainte-Catherine+St+W,+Montr%C3%A9al,+Communaut%C3%A9-Urbaine-de-Montr%C3%A9al,+Qu%C3%A9bec&amp;t=m&amp;ll=45.498406,-73.582821&amp;spn=0.042113,0.107288&amp;z=13\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nIl aime faire du vélo, cuire, le bilingualisme, visiter les ‘fameuses’ rapides de Lachine, et jouer à « répérer le Coupe Longueuil ».  Il l’haie quand des touries prononcent Montréal « Mawn-tree-all ».\n'), ('53', 'Vancouver', 'Canada', 'Located in beautiful Vancouver (birthplace of WonderProxy co-founder Paul Reinheimer), this server provides coverage to gets geo-sensitive applications in Western Canada and the Pacific North-West.  It is uncharacteristically forthcoming about the actual physical location of its datacenter.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?hl=en&amp;q=535+west+hastings,+vancouver+bc&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=535+W+Hastings+St,+Vancouver,+British+Columbia+V6B+1M1&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=49.290426,-123.119316&amp;spn=0.019593,0.053644&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?hl=en&amp;q=535+west+hastings,+vancouver+bc&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=535+W+Hastings+St,+Vancouver,+British+Columbia+V6B+1M1&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=49.290426,-123.119316&amp;spn=0.019593,0.053644&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not routing data, this server enjoys walking in Stanley Park, skiing on Grouse Mountain, and visiting the Capilano Suspension Bridge.  It hopes one day to see a sea otter with its own optics.', 'Situé dans la belle ville de Vancouver (ville natale de Paul Reinheimer, co-fondateur de WonderProxy), ce serveur fournit une bonne option pour les applications ciblées à l’Ouest Canadienne, ou le Nord-Ouest Pacifique en général.  Il est très ouvert avec sa situation géographique précise (exceptionnelle chez nos serveurs).\n\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?hl=fr&amp;q=535+west+hastings,+vancouver+bc&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=535+W+Hastings+St,+Vancouver,+British+Columbia+V6B+1M1&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=49.290426,-123.119316&amp;spn=0.019593,0.053644&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.Fr/maps?hl=fr&amp;q=535+west+hastings,+vancouver+bc&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=535+W+Hastings+St,+Vancouver,+British+Columbia+V6B+1M1&amp;gl=ca&amp;sqi=2&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=49.290426,-123.119316&amp;spn=0.019593,0.053644&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\nLorsqu’il ne dirige pas ses données, ce serveur aime se promener au Parc Stanley, faire du ski sur Mont Grouse, et visiter le pont Capilano.  Il espère un jour voir une loutre de mer avec ses propres optiques.'), ('54', 'Roubaix', 'France', 'This server is located in Roubaix, in the extreme north of France, on the border with Belgium.  With Paris, this server provides our presence for people looking to test GeoIP applications in France. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Roubaix,+France&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.113014,-94.614258&amp;sspn=9.116647,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Roubaix,+Nord,+Nord-Pas-de-Calais,+France&amp;t=m&amp;ll=53.041213,1.977539&amp;spn=9.255209,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Roubaix,+France&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.113014,-94.614258&amp;sspn=9.116647,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Roubaix,+Nord,+Nord-Pas-de-Calais,+France&amp;t=m&amp;ll=53.041213,1.977539&amp;spn=9.255209,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server is proud to have once hosted the results of the \'Roubaix 28 hours\', one of the longest walking races in the world, where people compete to see who can walk the furthest in 28 hours.  ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Roubaix, dans le Nord de la France, sur la frontière avec la Belgique.  Il est une moitié de notre réseau Française (avec Paris), et offre une bonne option pour tester les applications en dehors de la ville principale.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Roubaix,+France&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.113014,-94.614258&amp;sspn=9.116647,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Roubaix,+Nord,+Nord-Pas-de-Calais,+France&amp;t=m&amp;ll=53.041213,1.977539&amp;spn=9.255209,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Roubaix,+France&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=39.113014,-94.614258&amp;sspn=9.116647,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Roubaix,+Nord,+Nord-Pas-de-Calais,+France&amp;t=m&amp;ll=53.041213,1.977539&amp;spn=9.255209,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\nCe serveur est fière d’avoir—dans les passé—listé les résultats du Roubaix 28 heures, une des plus longues courses à pieds au monde, où les participants voient qui peut marcher la plus longue distance en 28 heures.'), ('55', 'Kansas City', 'United States', 'This server is located in Kansas City, Missouri.  For developers using GeoIP targeted at the central United States, this is a great server choice. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kansas+City,+KS,+United+States&amp;aq=1&amp;sll=29.424122,-98.493628&amp;sspn=0.639933,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=San+Antonio,+TX,+USA&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kansas+City,+Wyandotte,+Kansas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=44.715514,-94.482422&amp;spn=21.854178,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kansas+City,+KS,+United+States&amp;aq=1&amp;sll=29.424122,-98.493628&amp;sspn=0.639933,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=San+Antonio,+TX,+USA&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kansas+City,+Wyandotte,+Kansas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=44.715514,-94.482422&amp;spn=21.854178,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys watching The Wizard of Oz, eating apples, and updating its fantasy baseball league.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Kansas Cite, au Missouri.  Pour les programmeurs qui se servent du GeoIP ciblée au centre des États-Unis, c’est une bonne option.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kansas+City,+KS,+United+States&amp;aq=1&amp;sll=29.424122,-98.493628&amp;sspn=0.639933,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=San+Antonio,+TX,+USA&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kansas+City,+Wyandotte,+Kansas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=44.715514,-94.482422&amp;spn=21.854178,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kansas+City,+KS,+United+States&amp;aq=1&amp;sll=29.424122,-98.493628&amp;sspn=0.639933,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=San+Antonio,+TX,+USA&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Kansas+City,+Wyandotte,+Kansas,+United+States&amp;t=m&amp;ll=44.715514,-94.482422&amp;spn=21.854178,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime écouter Le Magicien d’Oz, manger des pommes, et mettre à jour son page de Fantasy Baseball.\n'), ('56', 'Hyderabad', 'India', 'This server is located in Hyderabad, India, and rounds out our coverage in India.  The city of Hyderabad is home to the Indian offices of many major IT companies, so it\'s a great choice for developers testing Geo-IP sensitive applications targeted at that demographic. <br><br>\n\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=hyderabad&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Hyderabad,+Ranga+Reddy,+Andhra+Pradesh,+India&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=21.043491,78.442383&amp;spn=14.323163,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=hyderabad&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Hyderabad,+Ranga+Reddy,+Andhra+Pradesh,+India&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=21.043491,78.442383&amp;spn=14.323163,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nOn its hours off, this server likes sneaking into the cafeterias of major IT companies for lunch, and perfecting its recipes for Hyderabadi Haleem and Hyderabadi Byriani.  ', null), ('57', 'Jakarta', 'Indonesia', 'This server is located in Jakarta, Indonesia.  Indonesia is the fourth-most populous country in the world, and Jakarta is the tenth-largest city in the world, so this server is a great option for testing GeoIP applications targeted at a large number of people.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Jakarta,+Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.044438,-10.634766&amp;sspn=38.690411,79.013672&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;t=m&amp;ll=2.108899,106.787109&amp;spn=30.379134,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Jakarta,+Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.044438,-10.634766&amp;sspn=38.690411,79.013672&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;t=m&amp;ll=2.108899,106.787109&amp;spn=30.379134,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not routing your data, this server enjoys getting out of Jakarta and travelling to the various islands that form Indonesia.  Thus far, it has particularly enjoyed relaxing its processor in Bali, and scuba diving in <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wakatobi_National_Park\">Wakatobi National Park</a>.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Jakarta, en Indonésie.  Indonésie est la quatrième plus importante pays au monde par population, et Jakarta est la dixième ville mondiale, ce qui rend ce serveur une excellente option pour tester des application GeoIP ciblées à des populations diverses.\n\n	<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Jakarta,+Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.044438,-10.634766&amp;sspn=38.690411,79.013672&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;t=m&amp;ll=2.108899,106.787109&amp;spn=30.379134,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Jakarta,+Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.044438,-10.634766&amp;sspn=38.690411,79.013672&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Jakarta+Capital+Region,+Indonesia&amp;t=m&amp;ll=2.108899,106.787109&amp;spn=30.379134,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\n\nLorsqu’il ne dirige pas vos données, ce serveur aime quitter Jakarta pour visiter les autres régions de l’Indonésie.  Jusqu’à maintenant, il a aimé rester son processeur à Bali, et faire du scuba au <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wakatobi_National_Park\">Parc National de Wakatobi</a>.');
INSERT INTO `servers_details` VALUES ('58', 'Valencia', 'Spain', 'This server resides in Valencia, a beautiful city in the country of Spain.  With servers in Valencia and Barcelona, we\'re happy to help you ensure your GeoIP applications are working properly throughout the country. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Valencia,+Spain&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=62.443704,130.429688&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Valencia,+Province+of+Valencia,+Valencia,+Spain&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.228517,-2.548828&amp;spn=11.38568,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Valencia,+Spain&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=62.443704,130.429688&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Valencia,+Province+of+Valencia,+Valencia,+Spain&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.228517,-2.548828&amp;spn=11.38568,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nOn its hours off, this server enjoys watching football… watching football… and watching more football.  ', 'Ce serveur se situe à Valencie, une belle ville Espagnol.  Avec des serveurs à Barcelone et Valencie, nous sommes contentes de vous aider à vous assurez que vos applications fonctionnent correctement à travers ce pays.\n<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Valencia,+Spain&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=62.443704,130.429688&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Valencia,+Province+of+Valencia,+Valencia,+Spain&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.228517,-2.548828&amp;spn=11.38568,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Valencia,+Spain&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=62.443704,130.429688&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Valencia,+Province+of+Valencia,+Valencia,+Spain&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.228517,-2.548828&amp;spn=11.38568,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nEn repos, ce serveur aime écouter le soccer… écouter le soccer… et écouter encore plus du soccer.\n'), ('59', 'Christchurch', 'New Zealand', 'This server is located in Christchurch, in New Zealand\'s South Island.  It\'s a great option for ensuring that your GeoIP applications target kiwis (both the birds and the people) correctly. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;sspn=0.008986,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-40.680638,172.22168&amp;spn=11.658805,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;sspn=0.008986,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-40.680638,172.22168&amp;spn=11.658805,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys travelling around New Zealand – skiing in Wanaka, bungy jumping in Queenstown, visiting penguins and albatross in Dunedin, and occasionally venturing up to the North Island to wander around in \"Mordor\" (aka <a href=\"http://www.doc.govt.nz/parks-and-recreation/national-parks/tongariro/\">Tongariro National Park</a>).  It loves pineapple lumps, L&P, and blowing on pies, and hates being mistaken for an Australian.\r\n', 'Ce serveur est situé à Christchurch, dans l’Ile du Sud de la Nouvelle-Zélande.  Il est une option idéale pour vérifier que votre application GeoIP identifie correctement les kiwis (humaines et aviaires).\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;sspn=0.008986,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-40.680638,172.22168&amp;spn=11.658805,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;sspn=0.008986,0.01929&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Christchurch,+Canterbury,+New+Zealand&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-40.680638,172.22168&amp;spn=11.658805,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nCe serveur aime voyager dans la Nouvelle-Zélande – faire le ski à Wanaka et le bungy à Queenstown, visiter les pingouins et albatros à Dunedin, et (de temps en temps) faire du randonné à Mordor (soit, <a href=”http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tongariro_National_Park”>Le parc national de Tongariro</a>) dans l’Ile du Nord.  Il adore les ‘pineapple lumps’ (une friandise d’ananas), le L&P, et souffler sur les tartes, mais il déteste être pris pour un Australien.\n'), ('60', 'Graz', 'Austria', 'This server is located in Graz, Austria.  Graz is the second largest city in Austria (after Vienna), our second Austrian server (again, after Vienna), and a UNESCO World Heritage site, and a great option for testing GeoIP sensitive applications outside Austria\'s capital city.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=graz,+austria&amp;aq=&amp;sll=60.370429,5.361328&amp;sspn=11.660889,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Graz,+Styria,+Austria&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.639177,14.501953&amp;spn=9.965367,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=graz,+austria&amp;aq=&amp;sll=60.370429,5.361328&amp;sspn=11.660889,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Graz,+Styria,+Austria&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.639177,14.501953&amp;spn=9.965367,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys lording the superior weather Graz enjoys over its Viennese colleague, and riding the Graz public transit network (it has an inexplicable love of trams).', 'Ce serveur situé à Graz, la deuxième ville d’Autriche (après Vienne), est notre deuxième option en Autriche (après Vienne…), est listé sur la liste de patrimoine mondiale d’ONUESC, et est une excellente option idéale pour tester les applications GeoIP en dehors de la ville principale d’Autriche.\n<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=graz,+austria&amp;aq=&amp;sll=60.370429,5.361328&amp;sspn=11.660889,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Graz,+Styria,+Austria&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.639177,14.501953&amp;spn=9.965367,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=graz,+austria&amp;aq=&amp;sll=60.370429,5.361328&amp;sspn=11.660889,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Graz,+Styria,+Austria&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.639177,14.501953&amp;spn=9.965367,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime rappeler à son collègue à Vienne que Graz a un meilleur climat, et être passager sur le réseau de transport public de Graz (il an un grand amour pour les trains).'), ('61', 'Luxembourg', 'Luxembourg', 'This server is located in the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg.  Is your application correctly displaying in Luxembourgish (the official language of Luxembourg)?  This server will help you check your GeoIP-using application is working in this small portion of Europe.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Luxembourg&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-2.547988,106.567383&amp;sspn=25.214055,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Luxembourg&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.021858,5.559082&amp;spn=4.941709,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Luxembourg&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-2.547988,106.567383&amp;sspn=25.214055,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Luxembourg&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.021858,5.559082&amp;spn=4.941709,13.73291&amp;z=6\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server is bitter that Luxembourg enjoys an oceanic climate, but is landlocked.  It enjoys informing all and sundry that Luxembourg sells the most alcohol per capita in Europe (while obscuring the fact that most is purchased by visitors from outside the country), visiting the National Museum of History and Art, and chatting with friends in the more than 17 datacentres located within the country.', 'Ce serveur se situe dans le duché de Luxembourg.  Est-ce que votre application change correctement de langue à Luxembourgeois (la langue officiel de Luxembourg)?  Ce serveur peut vous aider à vérifer si votre application GeoIP opère correctement dans ce coin de l’Europe.\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?\nf=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Luxembourg&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-2.547988,106.567383&amp;sspn=25.214055,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Luxembourg&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.021858,5.559082&amp;spn=4.941709,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Luxembourg&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=-2.547988,106.567383&amp;sspn=25.214055,39.506836&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Luxembourg&amp;t=m&amp;ll=50.021858,5.559082&amp;spn=4.941709,13.73291&amp;z=6\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur trouve très injuste le fait que Luxembourg a un climat océanique, même si c’est enclavé.  Il aime publier le fait que Luxembourg vend le plus grand quantité d’alcool par personne en Europe (tout en cachant que la majorité des achats sont faites par les visiteurs de l’étranger), visiter la Musée nationale d’art et d’histoire, et bavarder avec ses amis dans plus de 17 centres de données situées autour du pays.\n'), ('62', 'Cairo', 'Egypt', 'Cairo provides our Egyptian proxy, perfect for GeoIP testing this currently tumultuous region. Besides being the largest city in Egypt, Cairo is the home of the world\'s second oldest institute of higher learning: <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Al-Azhar_University\">Al-Azhar University</a>.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=cairo&amp;aq=&amp;sll=47.498406,19.040758&amp;sspn=0.496372,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cairo,+Egypt&amp;t=m&amp;ll=36.527295,27.246094&amp;spn=24.630798,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=cairo&amp;aq=&amp;sll=47.498406,19.040758&amp;sspn=0.496372,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cairo,+Egypt&amp;t=m&amp;ll=36.527295,27.246094&amp;spn=24.630798,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys mocking tourists who fly halfway around the world to see the pyramids, but go home with multitudes of pictures of the feral cats living in and about the various tombs and other tourist locations.', 'Caire fournit notre serveur proxy Égyptien, parfait pour tester dans cette région tumultueuse.  En plus d’être la plus grande ville de l’Afrique, <a href=\"http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Universit%C3%A9_al-Azhar\">l’université al-Azhar</a>, la deuxième plus ancienne institution d’enseignement supérieur au monde y est situé.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=cairo&amp;aq=&amp;sll=47.498406,19.040758&amp;sspn=0.496372,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cairo,+Egypt&amp;t=m&amp;ll=36.527295,27.246094&amp;spn=24.630798,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=cairo&amp;aq=&amp;sll=47.498406,19.040758&amp;sspn=0.496372,1.234589&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;gl=ca&amp;g=Budapest,+Hungary&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cairo,+Egypt&amp;t=m&amp;ll=36.527295,27.246094&amp;spn=24.630798,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\nCe serveur aime se moquer des touristes qui contournent le monde pour voir les pyramides, et retourne chez eux avec des tonnes de photos des chats sauvages qui vivent dans et autour des tombeaux. \n\n'), ('63', 'Fez', 'Morocco', 'This server is located in Fez (or Fès), the second-largest city in Morocco.  WonderProxy is happy to have this third option for GeoIP testing in Africa, along with Cairo, Egypt, and Cape Town, South Africa.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=49.823809,6.130371&amp;sspn=8.209177,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Fes,+Wilaya+de+Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;t=m&amp;ll=37.26531,-1.450195&amp;spn=12.230836,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=49.823809,6.130371&amp;sspn=8.209177,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Fes,+Wilaya+de+Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;t=m&amp;ll=37.26531,-1.450195&amp;spn=12.230836,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys wandering in the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medina_quarter\">medina</a>, the world largest contiguous car-free urban area, often while ironically wearing a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fez_(hat)\">Fez</a>.  It also enjoys visiting the oldest continuously functioning university in the world, the Unviersity of Al-Karaouine, and watching a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Big_Bang_(Doctor_Who)#Continuity\">selection of episodes of Doctor Who</a> in which its name is mentioned.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Fès, la deuxième ville du Maroc.  WonderProxy est heureux d’offrir une troisième option pour le testing GeoIP en Afrique, avec Caire en Égypte, et Cape-Town, en Afrique-du-Sud.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=49.823809,6.130371&amp;sspn=8.209177,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Fes,+Wilaya+de+Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;t=m&amp;ll=37.26531,-1.450195&amp;spn=12.230836,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=49.823809,6.130371&amp;sspn=8.209177,19.753418&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Fes,+Wilaya+de+Fes,+Fes-Boulemane,+Morocco&amp;t=m&amp;ll=37.26531,-1.450195&amp;spn=12.230836,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nCe serveur aime se promener à la médina, la plus grande région urbaine sans-autos au monde, souvent en portant ironiquement un fez.  Il aime également visiter la plus ancienne université du monde, <a href=\"http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quaraouiyine\">l’université al-Quaraouiyine</a>, et écouter une sélection d’émissions de Doctor Who où son nom est mentionné.\n'), ('64', 'Bangkok', 'Thailand', 'This server is located Bangkok, Thailand.  This server is a great option for getting GeoIP sensitive applications in Thailand, and in South-East Asia in general.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=bangkok,+thailand&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bangkok,+Thailand&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=21.371244,101.953125&amp;spn=28.395948,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?q=bangkok,+thailand&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bangkok,+Thailand&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=21.371244,101.953125&amp;spn=28.395948,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server enjoys watching the planes take off and land at Suvarnabhumi Airport.  It also enjoys cycling in Bangkok\'s many green spaces, and laughing at tourists who cockily order in restaurants, ignoring warnings from servers, then end up crying from the spiciness.', 'Ce serveur est situé à Bangkok, en Thaïlande.  Il est une bonne option pour vérifier les applications GeoIP à Thaïlande précisément, et généralement en Asie du Sud.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=bangkok,+thailand&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=fr&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bangkok,+Thailand&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=21.371244,101.953125&amp;spn=28.395948,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?q=bangkok,+thailand&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=fr&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Bangkok,+Thailand&amp;t=m&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ll=21.371244,101.953125&amp;spn=28.395948,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;source=embed\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\r\n<br><br>\n\rCe serveur aime regarder les décollages et atterrissages des avions à l’aéroport Suvarnabhum.  Il aime également faire du vélo dans les parcs de Bangkok, et rigoler auprès des touristes qui ignorent les avis des serveurs et finissent par pleurer à cause de la quantité d’épice dans les plats qu’ils on commandé.\r\n\n\n\n'), ('65', 'Hanoi', 'Vietnam', 'This server is located in Hanoi, Vietnam.  This is an excellent option to check that your GeoIP-using applications are working properly in Vietnam, and WonderProxy is happy to offer yet another option for application GeoIP testing in South-East Asia.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=hanoi,+vietnam&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Ho%C3%A0n+Ki%E1%BA%BFm,+Hanoi,+Vietnam&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,95.273438&amp;spn=49.582052,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=hanoi,+vietnam&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Ho%C3%A0n+Ki%E1%BA%BFm,+Hanoi,+Vietnam&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,95.273438&amp;spn=49.582052,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nThis server\'s hobbies include visiting the many historical landmarks within the city, shopping, and perfecting its recipe for phở.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Hanoï, au Vietnam.  Il est une excellente option pour vérifier que vos applications GeoIP marchent correctement au Vietnam.  WonderProxy est fière de vous offrir un autre option pour tester les applications GeoIP dans l\'Asie du Sud.\r<br><br>\r<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=hanoi,+vietnam&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Ho%C3%A0n+Ki%E1%BA%BFm,+Hanoi,+Vietnam&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,95.273438&amp;spn=49.582052,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=hanoi,+vietnam&amp;aq=&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Ho%C3%A0n+Ki%E1%BA%BFm,+Hanoi,+Vietnam&amp;t=m&amp;ll=34.885931,95.273438&amp;spn=49.582052,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\r<br><br>\r\rDans ses heures de pause, il aime visiter les lieux historiques de Hanoï, magasiner, et perfectionner son recette pour le phở.'), ('66', 'Istanbul', 'Turkey', 'This server is located in Istanbul, Turkey, the only city in WonderProxy\'s network (and indeed, in the world) that extends into two continents!  It\'s an excellent option to test that your GeoIP-sensitive application is working correctly in the multicultural city.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Istanbul,+Turkey&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=17.392579,106.699219&amp;sspn=23.501651,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Istanbul+Province%2FIstanbul,+Turkey&amp;t=m&amp;ll=43.961191,27.202148&amp;spn=11.070007,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Istanbul,+Turkey&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=17.392579,106.699219&amp;sspn=23.501651,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Istanbul+Province%2FIstanbul,+Turkey&amp;t=m&amp;ll=43.961191,27.202148&amp;spn=11.070007,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nWhen not routing your traffic, this server enjoys relaxing in the Hammams (Turkish baths), and cheering for the Fenerbahçe soccer team.\n', 'Ce serveur se situe à Istanbul en Turquie, la seule ville de notre réseau (en fait, la seule ville au monde) qui se retrouve sur deux continents (soit, l\'Europe et l\'Asie)!  Il est une excellente option pour tester les applications GeoIP dans cette ville multiculturelle.\n<br><br>\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Istanbul,+Turkey&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=17.392579,106.699219&amp;sspn=23.501651,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Istanbul+Province%2FIstanbul,+Turkey&amp;t=m&amp;ll=43.961191,27.202148&amp;spn=11.070007,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Istanbul,+Turkey&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=17.392579,106.699219&amp;sspn=23.501651,39.375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Istanbul+Province%2FIstanbul,+Turkey&amp;t=m&amp;ll=43.961191,27.202148&amp;spn=11.070007,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nLorsqu\'il ne dirige pas vos données, ce serveur aime relaxer aux Hammams (les bains turcs) et assister aux matches de l\'équipe de soccer Fenerbahçe.\n'), ('67', 'Bucharest', 'Romania', 'This server is located in Cluj-Napoca, Romania!  Romania is considered by many credit card processing agencies to be a high risk country for fraud - this proxy provides an excellent place to test that element of your code base, as well as elements using GeoIP. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj+County,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.106505,19.072266&amp;spn=18.946889,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj+County,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.106505,19.072266&amp;spn=18.946889,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen not routing your traffic and helping you test your GeoIP applications, this server enjoys giving tourists bad directions to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bran_Castle\">Bran Castle</a> and wandering in the central park.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Cluj-Napoca en Roumanie.  La Roumanie est considérée par beaucoup de compagnies de traitement de carte de crédit d’être un région d’haute risque de fraude; ce serveur vous offre une bonne opportunité de tester ce partie de votre code, et les applications GeoIP. <br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj+County,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.106505,19.072266&amp;spn=18.946889,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj,+Romania&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=39.184175,78.75&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Cluj-Napoca,+Cluj+County,+Romania&amp;t=m&amp;ll=52.106505,19.072266&amp;spn=18.946889,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nLorsqu\'il n\'est pas en train de diriger vos données ou de vous aider à tester vos applications GeoIP, ce serveur aime mal-diriger les touristes qui cherchent <a href=\"http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ch%C3%A2teau_de_Bran\">le château de Bran</a> et promener dans le parc central.'), ('68', 'Philadelphia', 'United States', 'This server is located in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, in the USA.  It is an excellent option for testing GeoIP-using applications that are targeted at Philadelphia, as well as providing yet another option for testing on the US East Coast.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=46.935261,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.102823,19.6875&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Philadelphie,+Comt%C3%A9+de+Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=41.47566,-76.333008&amp;spn=5.761422,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=46.935261,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.102823,19.6875&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Philadelphie,+Comt%C3%A9+de+Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=41.47566,-76.333008&amp;spn=5.761422,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small><br><br>\n\nWhen it\'s not directing your traffic, this server enjoys doing the Rocky run, and watching Philadelphia Flyers games.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Philadelphie, au Pensylvannie, aux États-Unis.  Il est une excellente option pour tester les applications GeoIP cliblées sur le Philadelphie, ainsi qu\'une option supplémentaire pour tester les applciations dans l\'Est Américaine.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=46.935261,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.102823,19.6875&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Philadelphie,+Comt%C3%A9+de+Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=41.47566,-76.333008&amp;spn=5.761422,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=46.935261,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.102823,19.6875&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Philadelphie,+Comt%C3%A9+de+Philadelphie,+Pennsylvanie,+%C3%89tats-Unis&amp;t=m&amp;ll=41.47566,-76.333008&amp;spn=5.761422,13.73291&amp;z=6&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nLorsqu\'il ne dirige pas vos données, ce serveur aime faire le trajet de course à pied de Rocky, et écouter les matches des Flyers de Philadelphie.\n'), ('69', 'Varna', 'Bulgaria', 'This server is located in Varna, Bulgaria, a seaside resort town on the Black Sea.  It\'s an excellent option for testing GeoIP applications in Bulgaria, as well as providing an extra option for testing in Eastern Europe in general.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.ca/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.237605,-75.531006&amp;sspn=4.52846,9.84375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.037868,20.742188&amp;spn=20.197452,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fcar/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.237605,-75.531006&amp;sspn=4.52846,9.84375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.037868,20.742188&amp;spn=20.197452,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View larger size</a></small>\n\n<br><br>\nIts hobbies include visiting the Varna Archeology Museum, and sending letters to our Miami server (Varna and Miami are twin cities).', 'Ce serveur se situe à Varna, en Bulgarie, une ville touristique au bord de la mer noire.  Il est une excellente option pour tester les applications GeoIP en Bulgarie, et fournit une autre option pour tester les applications dans l\'Europe orientale.\n<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.237605,-75.531006&amp;sspn=4.52846,9.84375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.037868,20.742188&amp;spn=20.197452,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;aq=0&amp;sll=40.237605,-75.531006&amp;sspn=4.52846,9.84375&amp;vpsrc=6&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Varna,+Bulgarie&amp;t=m&amp;ll=49.037868,20.742188&amp;spn=20.197452,54.931641&amp;z=4&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small>\n<br><br>\n\nComme passe-temps, ce serveur aime visiter la musée archéologique de Varna, et envoyer des lettres à notre server à Miami, puisse que Varna et Miami sont des villes jumelles.'), ('70', 'Santiago', 'Chile', 'This server is located in Santiago, Chile.  With it, we are happy to offer yet another option for GeoIP testing in South America.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Santiago+du+Chili,+Chili&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=Santiago&amp;sll=47.025206,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.133063,19.731445&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santiago+du+Chili,+R%C3%A9gion+m%C3%A9tropolitaine+de+Santiago,+Chili&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-18.979026,-72.246094&amp;spn=56.06631,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Santiago+du+Chili,+Chili&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=Santiago&amp;sll=47.025206,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.133063,19.731445&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santiago+du+Chili,+R%C3%A9gion+m%C3%A9tropolitaine+de+Santiago,+Chili&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-18.979026,-72.246094&amp;spn=56.06631,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View larger size</a></small><br><br>\n\nOn its downtime, this server enjoys hiking in the mountains and cycling in the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barrio_Bellavista\">Barrio Bellavista</a>.', 'Ce serveur se situe à Santiago de Chilie, en Chilie.  Nous sommes très heureux d\'offrir un autre option pour tester les applications GeoIP en Amérique du Sud.<br><br>\n\n<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Santiago+du+Chili,+Chili&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=Santiago&amp;sll=47.025206,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.133063,19.731445&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santiago+du+Chili,+R%C3%A9gion+m%C3%A9tropolitaine+de+Santiago,+Chili&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-18.979026,-72.246094&amp;spn=56.06631,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.fr/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Santiago+du+Chili,+Chili&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=Santiago&amp;sll=47.025206,1.73584&amp;sspn=8.133063,19.731445&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Santiago+du+Chili,+R%C3%A9gion+m%C3%A9tropolitaine+de+Santiago,+Chili&amp;t=m&amp;ll=-18.979026,-72.246094&amp;spn=56.06631,109.863281&amp;z=3&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">Agrandir le plan</a></small><br><br>\n\nEn pause, ce serveur aime faire du randonné dans les montagnes autour de la ville, et faire du vélo au <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barrio_Bellavista\">Barrio Bellavista</a>.'), ('71', 'Denver', 'United States', 'This server is located in Denver, Colorado, and provides an excellent option for testing GeoIP applications in the central United States. <br><br>\r\r<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Denver,+CO,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=denver,+co&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;sspn=0.008986,0.019269&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Denver,+Colorado&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.423457,-106.391602&amp;spn=11.350684,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Denver,+CO,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=denver,+co&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;sspn=0.008986,0.019269&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Denver,+Colorado&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.423457,-106.391602&amp;spn=11.350684,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A\" style=\"color:#0000FF;text-align:left\">View Larger Map</a></small>\r\r<br><br>\rWhen not routing your traffic, this server enjoys skiing and snowboarding, and Tebowing.\r', 'Ce serveur se situe à Denver, Colorado.  Il est un excellent option pour tester les application GeoIP dans le centre des États-Unis.<br><br>\r\r<iframe width=\"625\" height=\"350\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Denver,+CO,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=denver,+co&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;sspn=0.008986,0.019269&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Denver,+Colorado&amp;t=m&amp;ll=42.423457,-106.391602&amp;spn=11.350684,27.46582&amp;z=5&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed\"></iframe><br /><small><a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=embed&amp;hl=fr&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Denver,+CO,+United+States&amp;aq=0&amp;oq=denver,+co&amp;sll=43.673455,-79.455766&amp;